AmaMakedoni aya kwivoti kwi Referendum yokutshintsha igama lelizwe
Abavoti baza kuvota ngeCawa ukuba ilizwe labo lifanele litshintshwe igama libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia".
Oluvo lwabantu lwaqaliswa ukuze kusonjululwe imbambano eyayisele ikho kangangamashumi eminyaka neGrisi, eyayinephondo layo elibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.
IAthene sele ihlala igxininisa ukuba igama lommelwane wayo osenyakatho libonisa ukuba lifuna indawo yayo kwaye iye yaphikisana ngokuphindaphindiweyo nemibandela yayo yokuba lilungu le-EU neNATO.
UMongameli waseMakedoni uGjorge Ivanov, ongxamele ukuvota kweqela malunga nokutshintshwa kwegama, uthe uza kulibalela eli tyala.
Noko ke, abaxhasi be referendum, kuquka noNdunankulu uZoran Zaev, bathi ukutshintsha igama yintengo ekufuneka ihlawulwe ukuze ujoyine i-EU neNATO.
Iimbethe Zokuwa KukaMartin Ziyathula Njengamabandla KwiHarlem Struggle
UMnu. Adams wathi: "Ngokwembali, abantu abadala endithethe nabo bathi kwakukho ibha necawa kwikona nganye".
"Namhlanje, akukho nanye".
Wathi ukulahleka kweebha kwakungaqondakala.
Wathi: "Abantu namhlanje bahlalisana ngendlela eyahlukileyo".
Iibhari azisekho kwiindawo zokuhlala apho abantu beya rhoqo".
Ngokuphathelele iicawa, ukhathazekile kukuba imali evela ekuthengiseni iiasethi ayiyi kuhlala ixesha elide njengoko iinkokeli zilindele, "kwaye kungekudala okanye kamva ziya kubuyela kanye apho zaqala khona".
Wongezelela wathi, iicawa zinokutshintshwa zizakhiwo zeendawo zokuhlala ezineendawo zokuhlala ezizele ngabantu abangayi kunceda iindawo ezingcwele eziseleyo.
Wathi: "Abantu abaninzi abathenga iipropati ezihlala ezi zakhiwo baya kuba ngamadoda amhlophe, yaye ngenxa yoko baya kukhawuleza ukuba ezi cawa zivale ngokupheleleyo kuba kusenokwenzeka ukuba uninzi lwabantu abafudukela kwezi cawa aziyi kuba ngamalungu ezi cawa".
Omabini la mabandla akhiwa ngamabandla amhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe sisixeko esikhulu esimnyama - iMetropolitan Community ngowe-1870, iSt. Martin emva kweminyaka elishumi.
Ibandla lokuqala lamaMethodist elimhlophe lafuduka ngeminyaka yee - 1930.
Ibandla labamnyama elalikhonza kufuphi lafumana ilungelo lokwakha.
ISt. Martin's yathatyathwa libandla labamnyama phantsi koMfundisi uJohn Howard Johnson, owalathisa ukubhikisha abathengisi kwi-125th Street, eyona ndlela iphambili yokuthenga eHarlem, ababengafuni ukuqesha okanye ukukhuthaza abamnyama.
Umlilo ngowe-1939 washiya isakhiwo sonakele kakhulu, kodwa njengoko amalungu eqela likaBawo Johnson ayeceba ukwakha kwakhona, ayalela ukuba kusetyenziswe icarillon.
UMbingeleli Omkhulu uDavid Johnson, unyana kaBawo Johnson nomlandeli wakhe eSt. Martin's, ngokuzingca wabiza le carillon ngokuthi "ngamakhala abantu abangamahlwempu".
Ingcali eyayidlala ikariyon ngoJulayi yabiza le ngoma ngokuthi yenye into: "Luyigugu lenkcubeko" yaye "yindawo engazange ithathwe indawo yembali".
Ingcali, uTiffany Ng weYunivesithi yaseMichigan, yaqaphela nokuba yayiyinkqubo yokuqala ehlabathini yokudlala ikariyon ngomculi omnyama, uDiyonizio A. Lind, owafudukela kwikariyon enkulu kwiCawa yaseRiverside kwiminyaka eli-18 eyadlulayo.
UMnu Merriweather wathi iSt. Martin's ayizange imthimbe.
Oko kuye kwenzeka eSt. Martin's kwiinyanga ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo kuye kwaba libali eliyinkimbinkimbi labaqulunqi bezakhiwo nabaqeshi, abanye beziswa ziinkokeli zamalayi zecawa, abanye bevela kwicawa yamaBishopu.
I-Westry - eli qumrhu elilawulayo leparishi, elenziwe ziinkokeli zamalayi - yabhalela i-diocese ngoJulayi ikhathazekile kukuba i-diocese "iya kufuna ukudlulisela iindleko" kwi-Westry, nangona i-Westry yayingabandakanyekanga ekuqesheni abayili kunye nabaqeshi ababethunyelwe yi-diocese.
Abanye abantu becawa bakhalazela ukungabikho kokutyhila kwecawa.
I-shark ilimaza umntwana oneminyaka eli-13 ubudala ekuntywileni kwe-lobster eCalifornia
