Lo hlaselo lwenzeka ngaphambi nje kwe-7 kusasa kufuphi neBeacons Beach eEncinitas.
UChad Hammel uxelele iKSWB-TV eSan Diego ukuba ubekhe wabhabhaqa nabahlobo bakhe kangangeyure enesiqingatha ngoMgqibelo ekuseni xa weva inkwenkwe ikhala icela uncedo yaza emva koko yabhadula neqela ukuze incede imkhuphe emanzini.
UHammel wathi ekuqaleni wayecinga ukuba kukuchukumisa nje ukubamba ihlombe, kodwa "waqonda ukuba wayedanduluka esithi, 'Ndiye ndabethwa!
Ndilutshixiwe!'
