Izicwangciso zikaSainsbury zikhuthaza ukufikelela kwintengiso yobuhle yaseBritani
ISainsbury's ithatha iBoots, iSuperdrug neDebenhams ngeendawo zokunxiba ezenziwe ngevenkile eneenkonzo zobuhle ezixhotyiswe ngabasebenzi abaziingcali.
Njengenxalenye yokunyusa okukhulu kwimarike yobuhle yase-UK ene-Â£2.8 yezigidigidi, eqhubeka ikhula ngelixa ukuthengiswa kwefashoni kunye nezinto zasekhaya kuhla, iivenkile ezinkulu zobuhle ziya kuvavanywa kwiivenkile ezili-11 kulo lonke ilizwe kwaye zihanjiswe kwiivenkile ezininzi kunyaka ozayo ukuba ziya kuphumelela.
Olu tyalo-mali luza kuba iivenkile ezinkulu zifuna iindlela zokusebenzisa indawo esele zisetyenziswe kumabonwakude, kwii-microwave nakwizinto zasekhaya.
USainsbury's uthe uza kuphinda kabini ubungakanani bezinto eziza kuthengwa ngumzi mveliso wayo ukuze ube ziimveliso ezingama-3 000, kuquka iimveliso ezifana neRevlon, Essie, Tweezerman neDr. PawPaw okokuqala ngqa.
Iindawo ezikhoyo ezivela kwiL'Oreal, iMaybelline neBurt's Bees nazo ziya kufumana indawo engakumbi kunye neendawo ezibhalwe ngomqondiso ofana nezo zifumaneka kwiivenkile ezinjengeBoots.
Le ntengiso iphinda isebenzise i-boutique yayo ukuze ininzi yeemveliso zayo ibe zixhamle abantu abangamakhwenkwe - nto leyo efunwa ngakumbi ngabathengi abaselula.
Ukongezelela, ivenkile yeparfume iFragrance Shop iza kuvavanya iivenkile ezimbini zeSainsbury, eyokuqala yazo yavula eCroydon, kumzantsi weLondon, kwiveki ephelileyo ngoxa eyesibini yavula eSelly Oak, eBirmingham, kamva kulo nyaka.
Ukuthenga nge-intanethi nokutshintsha kwendlela yokuthenga ukutya okuncinane imihla ngemihla kwiivenkile zendawo kuthetha ukuba iivenkile ezinkulu kufuneka zenze okungakumbi ukuze zikhuthaze abantu ukuba batyelele.
UMike Coupe, umphathi omkhulu weSainsbury's, uthe ezi ndawo ziya kujonga njengeivenkile ezinkulu njengoko le nkampani izama ukulwa neAldi neLidl eneenkonzo ezininzi kunye nezokutya ezingaphaya.
ISainsbury's ibeka iArgos kwiivenkile ezingamakhulu kwaye iye yazisa neendawo zokuhlala ezininzi ukususela ekuthengeni zombini ezi nkampani kwiminyaka emibini edluleyo, nto leyo ithi iye yaqinisa ukuthengisa ukutya kwaye yenza ukufunyanwa kwayo kwaba yingenelo ngakumbi.
Umzamo wangaphambili wale supermarket wokulungisa amacandelo ayo obuhle neekhemesti waphela.
ISainsbury's yavavanya umbutho wokubambisana neBoots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yama-2000, kodwa ukudibana kwaphela emva kwengxabano malunga nendlela yokwahlula ingeniso kwiivenkile zeekhemikhali kwiivenkile zayo ezinkulu.
Eli qhinga litsha liza emva kokuba iSainsbury's ithengise ishishini layo leekhemesti levenkile ezingama-281 kuCelesio, umnini womxokelelwane weLloyds Pharmacy, nge-Â£125 yezigidi, kwiminyaka emithathu edluleyo.
Ithi uLloyds uza kudlala indima kule nkqubo, ngokongeza uluhlu olongezelelekileyo lweempawu zokhathalelo lolusu ezinje ngeLa Roche-Posay neVichy kwiivenkile ezine.
UPaul Mills-Hicks, umlawuli wezentengiso eSainsbury, wathi: "Sitshintshe indlela ezibonakala ngayo izitulo zethu ukuze kubonakale bhetele kubathengi bethu.
Kwakhona siye safumana oogxa abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo abaza kuba khona ukuze banike iingcebiso.
Uluhlu lwethu lweempawu zenzelwe ukuba zilungele zonke iimfuno yaye imeko entle kunye neendawo ezifanelekileyo zenza ukuba ngoku sibe yindawo entle yokuthenga izinto eziyingozi".
UPeter Jones 'ucaphukile' emva kokuba uHolly Willoughby etshatile kwi-11 yezigidi zeedola
Inkwenkwezi yeDragons Den uPeter Jones ushiye 'uFurious' emva kokuba umboneleli weTV uHolly Willoughby ehoxise isivumelwano se-Â£ 11 yezigidi kunye neshishini lakhe lemveliso yokuphila ukuze agxile kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha neMarks neSpencer kunye ne-ITV
UWilloughby akanalo ixesha lokunxiba iimpahla zasekhaya kunye nezithako ze-truly.
Ishishini lale ndoda lalifaniswa neGwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand.
Lo mfo usasazayo, oneminyaka engama-37, wathumela kwi-Instagram ukuvakalisa ukuba uyahamba.
UHolly Willoughby ushiye inkwenkwezi yeDragons' Den uPeter Jones ebulaleka ngokuyeka ishishini labo eliyingenelo lokwenza uphawu lwendlela yokuphila ngomzuzu wokugqibela - ukuze agxile kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha ze-bumper neMarks & Spencer ne-ITV.
Imithombo ithi uJones "wayesithi khunubembe" xa intombazana yegolide yeTV yavuma ngexesha lentlanganiso enzima ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu loshishino lwakhe eMarlow, eBuckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano zayo ezintsha - ezixabisa ukuya kuthi ga kwizigidi ezili-1.5 ze-Â£ - zazisithi ayisekho ixesha elaneleyo lokuzinikezela kwiimpahla zasekhaya kunye nezixhobo ze-truly brand.
Ishishini lalinganiswa neGwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand kwaye lalinomvuzo ophindwe kabini weWilloughby's Â£11 million.
Njengoko uWilloughby, oneminyaka engama-37, wathumela kwi-Instagram ukuvakalisa ukuba uyemka kuTruly, uJones waphuma eBritani waya kwenye yeendawo zakhe zokuhlala.
Omnye umthombo wathi: "Enyanisweni yayikukude lee kwizinto ezazibalulekile kuHolly.
Kwakuza kuba likamva lakhe elide elaliza kumbona kwiminyaka emibini elandelayo.
Isigqibo sakhe sokushiya wonke umntu owayeneentlungu sothusa.
Akukho mntu wakholwayo ngoko kwakusenzeka ngoLwesibini, kwakusondele gqitha ekuqaliseni.
Kukho indawo yokugcina impahla ezele ziimpahla kwi-Marlow HQ ezilungele ukuthengiswa".
Iingcali zikholelwa ekubeni ukuhamba komntu owenza le ntetho ye-This Morning, ongomnye weenkwenkwezi zaseBritani ezixabisa kakhulu, kunokubiza inkampani izigidi ngenxa yotyalo-mali oluninzi kwiimveliso ezisusela kumathanga neenkwenkwezi ukuya kwiimpahla nakwimpahla yasekhaya, yaye kusenokubakho ukulibaziseka ngakumbi ekuqalisweni kwayo.
Yaye oko kusenokuthetha ukuphela kobuhlobo obude.
Umama wabantwana abathathu uWilloughby nomyeni wakhe uDan Baldwin bebesondele kuJones nomfazi wakhe uTara Capp kangangeminyaka elishumi.
UWilloughby waseka iTruly kunye noCapp ngo-2016 kwaye uJones, oneminyaka engama-52, wajoyina njengesihlalo ngoMatshi.
Esi sibini sivakasha kunye yaye uJones uneshishini lama-40 ekhulwini kwinkampani kaBaldwin yokuvelisa umabonwakude.
UWilloughby uza kuba ngummeli weM & S kwaye uza kuthatha indawo kaAnt McPartlin njengombonisi we-ITV's I'm A Celebrity.
Umthombo osondele kuJones wathi izolo ebusuku "asifuni kuthetha ngemicimbi yakhe yeshishini".
