Nangona abantu abangaphezu kwe-10 ekhulwini babekhe baphulukana nomhlaba, akukho ntlekele yasekuhlaleni yabhengezwa, nto leyo eyayiyimfuneko ukuze kuncedwe amazwe ngamazwe.
"Ngelishwa, kwiimeko ezininzi, baye bacaca ukuba abaceli uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe, ngoko kunzima", utshilo uNksz Sumbung.
Ngoxa i-Save the Children isenza iqela lokuya ePalu, akuqinisekwanga ukuba abasebenzi bamanye amazwe banokusebenza emhlabeni.
UMnu Sutopo, isithethi se-arhente yelizwe yeentlekele, uthe amagosa ase-Indonesia ayavavanya imeko ePalu ukuze abone ukuba ngaba amaziko amazwe ngamazwe aya kuvunyelwa ukuba anikele kumzamo wokunceda.
Ngenxa yokunyikima komhlaba okuhlala kuqhubeka eIndonesia, eli lizwe alilungelanga kakuhle ukujamelana nengqumbo yendalo.
Nangona iindawo zokukhusela amaza e-tsunami ziye zakhiwa e-Aceh, aziqhelekanga kwezinye iindawo eziselunxwemeni.
Nangona kwakukho isilumkiso, kusenokwenzeka ukuba ukungabikho kwesirena esisilumkiso se-tsunami ePalu kwabangela ukuba abantu abaninzi bafe.
Ngamaxesha amnandi, ukuhamba phakathi kweziqithi ezininzi zaseIndonesia kunzima.
Iintlekele zemvelo zenza izinto zibe nzima ngakumbi.
Inqanawa yesibhedlele eyayibekwe eLombok ukuze inyamekele amaxhoba enyikima iya ePalu, kodwa kuya kuthatha iintsuku ezintathu ukuya kwindawo eyenzeke kuyo le ntlekele intsha.
UMongameli uJoko Widodo wenza ukuphucula iziseko ezingasebenzi kakuhle zaseIndonesia ibe yinxalenye ephambili yomkhankaso wakhe wokhetho, yaye uye wachitha imali eninzi kwiindlela nakumajelo kaloliwe.
Kodwa ukusilela kwemali kuye kwaphazamisa ulawulo lukaMnu. Joko njengoko ephinda elungelwe ukhetho kunyaka ozayo.
UMnu. Joko naye ujongene nengcinezelo evela kwiingxabano zamahlelo e-Indonesia, apho amalungu amaninzi amaSilamsi aye amkela uhlobo oluthile lokholo olungagqithiyo.
