Jonga: UDaniel Sturridge waseLiverpool uphosa umlinganisi onzulu nxamnye neChelsea
UDaniel Sturridge wasindisa iLiverpool kwi-Premier League elahlekileyo kwi-Chelsea ngentsimbi kumzuzu wama-89 ngoMgqibelo eStamford Bridge eLondon.
USturridge wafumana ipasi evela kuXherdan Shaqiri ngelixa malunga neeyadi ezingama-30 ukusuka kwinjongo yeChelsea neqela lakhe libuyela emva nge-1: 0.
Waya kwicala lasekhohlo ngaphambi kokuba athathe umpu aye kumgangatho ongaphaya.
Eli phulo lalihamba phezulu kwebhokisi njengoko lalihamba liye kwikona ephezulu yasekunene yomnatha.
Ekugqibeleni ibhola yawa phezu kweKepa Arrizabalaga eyayigxuma yaza yawa kumnatha.
"Kwakungokuzama nje ukufikelela kuloo ndawo, ukufikelela kwibhola kwaye abadlali abanjengoShaq bahlala beyibetha phambili kangangoko kunokwenzeka, ngoko ndazama ukuzenzela ixesha elininzi kangangoko kunokwenzeka", utshilo uSturridge kwiLiverpoolFC.com.
"Ndabona uKante esiza ndaza ndathinta ndayeka ukucinga kakhulu ndaza ndatshaya".
I-Chelsea yahola nge-1-0 kwisiqingatha semizuzu emva kokufumana amanqaku kumzuzu wama-25 kwi-star yaseBelgian u-Eden Hazard.
Umhlaseli weBlues wafumana umngcelele kuMatteo Kovacic kuloo mdlalo, ngaphambi kokuba aphenduke kufuphi nomphakathi webala aze aphumelele kwisiqingatha seLiverpool.
UKovacic wenza umzamo omncinane kwicandelo eliphakathi.
Emva koko wadlala ibhola entle, ekhokelela uHazard kwibhokisi.
UHazard wadlula ekuvikeleni waza wagqiba ekumngxunyeni kwindawo ekude enetheni ngomlenze wasekhohlo edlula uAlisson Becker waseLiverpool.
ILiverpool iya kudibana neNaples kwisigaba samagrupha seChampions League ngo-3:00 emva kwemini ngoLwesithathu eStadio San Paolo eNaples, eItali.
I-Chelsea iya kudibana neVideoton kwi-UEFA Europa League ngo-3:00 emva kwemini ngoLwesine eLondon.
Inani labafileyo kwi-tsunami yaseIndonesia lenyuka laya kutsho kuma-832
Inani labantu ababuleweyo kunyikima kunye netsunami eIndonesia liye lafikelela kuma-832, ngokutsho kwequmrhu elilawula iintlekele kweli lizwe ekuseni ngeCawa.
Abantu abaninzi baxelwa ukuba bangena kwiingxangxasi zezakhiwo eziwileyo kwinyikima yehlabathi enamandla angama-7.5 eyahlasela ngoLwesihlanu yaza yabangela amaza aphakamileyo ukuya kutsho kwiimitha ezingama-20, utshilo isithethi searhente uSutopo Purwo Nugroho kwinkomfa yeendaba.
Isixeko sasePalu, esinabantu abangaphezu kwama - 380 000, sasigcwele imingxuma yezakhiwo eziwileyo.
Amapolisa abamba indoda eneminyaka engama-32 ngokusola ukubulala emva kokuba ibhinqa lityakatyiwe labulawa
Kuqalwe uphando lokubulala emva kokuba umzimba womfazi wafunyanwa eBirkenhead, eMersayide namhlanje ekuseni.
Lo mfo oneminyaka engama-44 ubudala wafunyanwa ngo-7: 55 ekuseni eneentlungu zokuphanga kwiGrayson Mews eJohn Street, kunye nendoda eneminyaka engama-32 ubudala ebekwa ityala lokubulala.
Amapolisa abongoza abantu abahlala kuloo ndawo ababone okanye beve nantoni na ukuba beze.
UGqwetha uBrian O'Hagan wathi: 'Uphando lukwamanqanaba okuqala kodwa ndingathanda ukuba nabani na osondele kuJohn Street eBirkenhead obone okanye eve into esolisayo aqhagamshelane nathi.
Ndicela nokuba nabani na, ingakumbi abaqhubi beeteksi, abanokuba babambe nantoni na kwi-dashcam ukuba banxibelelane nathi njengoko banokuba nolwazi olubalulekileyo kuphando lwethu".
Umthetheli wamapolisa uqinisekisile ukuba ibhinqa elafunyanwa lingumntu wasekuhlaleni eBirkenhead yaye lafunyanwa ngaphakathi kwepropathi.
Namhlanje emva kwemini abahlobo bakholelwa ukuba bayamazi lo mfazi bafike kwindawo apho kwenzeka khona le nto ukuze babuze ukuba wafunyanwa phi namhlanje ekuseni.
Iipolisa zithi ziza kuxelela izalamane ezisondeleyo zomntu owaswelekayo.
Umqhubi weteksi ohlala eGrayson Mews usandul' ukuzama ukubuyela kwindlu yakhe kodwa uxelelwa ngamapolisa ukuba akukho mntu uvumelekileyo ukungena okanye ukuphuma kwisakhiwo.
Wayengakwazi ukuthetha xa efumanisa oko kwenzekileyo.
Abemi ngoku baxelelwa ukuba kuza kudlula iiyure ngaphambi kokuba babuyele.
Kwasiwa ipolisa lixelela enye indoda ukuba ngoku yonke loo ndawo iphathwa njengendawo yokuqhekeka.
Kwabonakala ibhinqa lilila.
Uhlala esithi 'kubi gqitha.'
Ngentsimbi yesibini emva kwemini, iivani ezimbini zamapolisa zazikwicandelo eliphakathi, kunye nenye ivenkile eyayiphambi nje.
Amanye amagosa ayemi ngaphakathi kwelo cordon egcina iliso kwibhokisi yezakhiwo.
