Isikhumbuzo sikaCromwell sePalamente siyeyona ndawo yokugqibela 'yokubuyisela imbali'
Ukugxothwa kwayo kwakuya kuba bubulungisa obungathi buchanekile bokutshatyalaliswa kwakhe njengeTaliban kwezinto ezininzi zokwakha nezonqulo zaseNgilani ezenziwa ngabalandeli bakhe abangamaPuritan.
Kodwa iCromwell Society yachaza isiluleko sikaMnu Crick ngokuthi "sisidenge" yaye "sisizama ukuhlaziya imbali".
UJohn Goldsmith, usihlalo weCromwell Society, wathi: "Kwakungenakuphepheka ukuba kwingxoxo yangoku ngokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo ukuba umfanekiso kaOliver Cromwell ngaphandle kweNdlu yaseWestminster ube yinjongo.
I-iconoclasm yeemfazwe zaseNgilani zange ilawulwe okanye yenziwe nguCromwell.
Mhlawumbi uCromwell ongalunganga wayeza kunikelwa ngenxa yezenzo zomkhulu wakhe uThomas kwinkulungwane edluleyo.
Umfanekiso kaCromwell obalaseleyo kaSir William Hamo Thorneycroft ubonisa ukuba wenziwa ngenkulungwane ye-19 yaye yinxalenye yembali yomntu abaninzi abakholelwa ukuba ufanelekile ukuwubhiyozela.
UMnu Goldsmith waxelela iThe Sunday Telegraph: "UCromwell wayebonwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ngakumbi ekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-19 kunangoku, njengomkhuseli wepalamente nxamnye noxinzelelo lwangaphandle, kwimeko yakhe ngokuqinisekileyo yayikukumkanikazi.
Ukuba oko kungumzekeliso ochanekileyo ngokupheleleyo yinto eqhubeka ingxoxo yembali.
Into eqinisekileyo kukuba ingxabano yangasekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-17 iye yavelisa uphuhliso oluzayo lwesizwe sethu, yaye uCromwell ngumntu owaziwayo owenza icala elinye laloo mahluko.
Iimpumelelo zakhe njengoMkhuseli weNkosi nazo zifanele zibhiyozelwe kwaye zikhunjulwe".
Ingulube Ebulalayo Ibulala Umlimi WaseTshayina
Ngokutsho kweendaba zasekuhlaleni, umfama wahlaselwa waza wabulawa yingulube kwintengiso kumzantsi-ntshona weTshayina.
Indoda, eyaziwa ngegama layo elingu "Yuan", yafunyanwa ifile ine-artery enqunyulwe, igutyungelwe ligazi kufuphi ne-sty kwimarike yaseLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou, lapapasha iSouth China Morning Post ngeCawa.
Umfuyi wehagu ulungiselela ukufaka iintsholongwane kwiingulube kwindawo yokugcina iihagu ngoMeyi 30, 2005 eXining kwiPhondo laseQinghai, eChina.
Kubikwa ukuba wahamba nomzala wakhe esuka kwiphondo elingummelwane laseYunnan ngoLwesithathu ukuya kuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 kwimarike.
Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana efile, waza wafumanisa ucango lwehagu elingummelwane luvulekile.
Wathi kwakukho ingulube enkulu enegazi emlonyeni wayo.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo, ukuhlolwa kweengcali zamatyala kwaqinisekisa ukuba le ngulube yayimalunga neekhilogram ezingama-550 yayimxhele umfama de wafa.
"Iimilenze yomzala wam yayinegazi yaye inqunywe", watsho umzala, ekuthiwa nguWu, njengoko kuchazwe kwiGuiyang Evening News.
Umfanekiso weekhamera zokhuseleko ubonisa uYuan engena kwimarike ngo-4:40 ekuseni ngoLwesine ukuze ondle iihagu zakhe.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa malunga neyure kamva.
Isilwanyana esabulala loo ndoda sasingeyomntu kaYuan okanye umzala wakhe.
Umphathi wentengiso waxelela i-Evening News ukuba le ngulube yayikwicala ukuze ingahlaseli nabani na, ngoxa amapolisa ayeqokelela ubungqina kwindawo eyenzekayo.
Kusithiwa intsapho kaYuan kunye nabasemarikeni bathetha ngembuyekezo yokufa kwakhe.
Nangona kunqabile, kuye kwabhalwa ngamaxesha okuhlaselwa kwabantu ziingulube.
Ngowe-2016, ingulube yahlasela ibhinqa nomyeni walo kwifama yabo eMassachusetts, ishiya indoda inemivumbo enzima.
Kwiminyaka elishumi eyadlulayo, ingulube eneekhilogram ezingama-650 yaqhekeza umfama waseWales kwitrektara yakhe de umfazi wakhe wayisoyika le nkomo.
Emva kokuba umfama waseOregon etyiwe ziingulube zakhe ngo-2012, umfama waseManitoba uxelele iCBC News ukuba iihagu azihlali zinobundlobongela kodwa incasa yegazi ingasebenza "njengomkhuthazi".
"Baneentloni nje.
Zizinto eziphazamisayo, zifuna ukwazi ngakumbi... azikufuni ukukwenzakalisa.
Kufuneka nje ubahlonele ngokwaneleyo", watsho.
Iintsalela zeNkanyamba uRosa ziza kuzisa imvula enamandla kumazantsi ntshona eUnited States
Njengoko kuqikelelwa, iNkanyamba uRosa iya buthathaka njengoko ihamba phezu kwamanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, uRosa uza kuzisa izantyalantyala zemvula kumantla eMexico nakumazantsi ntshona eUnited States kwiintsuku ezizayo.
URosa wayenomoya onamandla angama - 85 mph, iNkanyamba yoMgangatho 1, ukususela nge - 5 ekuseni ngeCawa yaseMpuma, yaye yayikwimimandla engama - 385 miles kumzantsi - ntshona wePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa aye emantla ngeCawa.
Okwangoku, umlambo uqalisa ukuma phezu koLwandlekazi iPasifiki uze uqhubele empuma ukuya kunxweme olusentshona yeUnited States. Njengoko uRosa esondela kwiNhlonhlo yaseBaja California ngoMvulo njengesaqhwithi esishushu siya kuqalisa ukuqhubela umswakama osenyakatho osenyakatho ukuya kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States.
URosa uza kuzisa imvula efikelela kwii-intshi ezili-10 kwiindawo ezithile zaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, ukufuma kwelitropiki okudibana nomngxuma osondelayo kuya kubangela imvula eninzi ehla kumzantsi-ntshona kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Kwindawo ethile, imvula engama - 1 ukuya kuma - 4 intshi iya kubangela izikhukula eziyingozi, ukugeleza kwezinto ezilahlekileyo kunye nokukhukhula komhlaba entlango.
Umswakama onzulu wamanzi ashushu uya kubangela ukuba imvula ibe ngama - 2 ukusa kuma - 3 e - inches ngeyure kwiindawo ezithile, ingakumbi kumacandelo asezantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kucelwa ukuba kubekho imvula engange - 2 ukuya kutsho kwi - 4 intshi kwiindawo eziseMzantsi - Ntshona, ingakumbi kwiindawo ezininzi zaseArizona.
Ukutshatyalaliswa kwezikhukula kungenzeka xa iimeko zisiya zisiba mbi ngenxa yemvula etshisayo.
Akuyi kuba luncedo kakhulu ukuphuma entlango uhamba ngeenyawo usongelwa yimvula etshisayo.
Imvula enamandla inokwenza imingxuma ibe yimilambo enomsindo yaye izivunguvungu ziya kuzisa imimoya enamandla nomoya othuthuzelayo.
Umlambo osondelayo uza kuzisa imvula enzulu kwiindawo ezithile zonxweme lwaseMzantsi California.
Kukho imvula engaphezulu kwe - 6 cm, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba kubekho ukuchitheka okuncinane kwezinto ezingasebenziyo neendlela ezicothayo.
Le yayiza kuba yimvula yokuqala kwelo phondo ngexesha labo lemvula.
Ezinye iimvula ezitshatyalaliswe ngamaxesha ashushu ezishushu ziya kuqala ukusondela eArizona ngasekupheleni kweCawa nangentsasa yangoMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula isasazeke ngakumbi ngasekupheleni koMvulo nangoLwesibini.
Imvula eninzi iya kusasazeka kwiiKona ezine ngoLwesibini ize iqhubeke kude kube ngoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha, amaqondo obushushu asebenza ngamandla aseMerika njengoko iArctic iphola, kodwa amaqondo obushushu asezindaweni ezishushu ahlala efudumele.
Maxa wambi oku kukhokelela kutshintsho olukhulu lobushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Kukho umzekelo omhle wokwahluka kobushushu obukhulu kumbindi weUnited States ngeCawa.
Kukho umahluko obungama - 20 degrees obandayo phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, nakuma - St. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu obuhlala buhleli behlobo buza kuzama ukwakha nokwandisa kwakhona.
Uninzi lwe-US esembindini nasempuma kulindeleke ukuba lubone ukuqala okufudumeleyo kuka-Oktobha kunye nama-80s asasazeke ngokubanzi ukusuka kumaThafa aseMzantsi ukuya kwiindawo zaseMntla-mpuma.
Isixeko saseNew York sinokufikelela kwi-80 degrees ngoLwesibini, nto leyo eya kuba ngama-10 degrees ngaphezu komlinganiselo.
Isibikezelo sethu sezulu sexesha elide sibonisa amathuba aphezulu okuba amaqondo obushushu angaphezulu komlinganiselo kwimpuma yeUnited States ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala sikaOktobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele uBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ubungqina obumangalisayo ngoLwesine bomntu okhethwe kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh nomfazi owayemtyhola ngokumhlasela ngokwesini ekuthiwa kwenzeka kwiminyaka yoo-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford, kumajelo amathandathu eendaba.
Okwangoku, umzabalazo wezopolitiko waqhubeka, kunye nabasasazi beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba beendaba eziqhelekileyo ukuze bafumane umyalezo womhla kaLwesihlanu womzuzu wokugqibela: isivumelwano esenziwe ngumongameli waseArizona uJeff Flake sokuba i-FBI ihambe iphando lweveki enye malunga nezityholo.
UFord uxelele iKomiti yezoBulungisa yeSenate ukuba uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba uKavanaugh wamchukumisa enxilile waza wazama ukumkhulula kwiqela lasesikolweni.
UKavanaugh, xa wayevuma, wathi uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba akuzange kwenzeke.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20.4 abaxelwe nguNielsen ngoLwesihlanu bayibukele.
Inkampani yayibalwa umlinganiselo wababukeli kwi-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye ne-MSNBC.
Amanani awazange afumaneke ngoko nangoko kwamanye amanethiwekhi, kuquka i-PBS, i-C-SPAN neFox Business Network.
Yaye uNilsen ubedla ngokuba neengxaki zokulinganisa abantu ababukela kwiiofisi.
Ukuze sikwenze oko, oko kukuthi, ubukhulu babaphulaphuli obufana nobomdlalo webhola ekhatywayo okanye owama-Academy Awards.
I-Fox News Channel, eneengcali ezixhasa kakhulu ukuqeshwa kukaKavanaugh, yalawula zonke iinethiwekhi ezinokubukela abantu abazizigidi ezingama-5.69 ngexesha lokuva imini yonke, utshilo uNilsen.
I-ABC yaba ngowesibini ngezigidi ezingama-3.26 zabukeli.
I-CBS yayinezigidi eziyi-3.1, i-NBC yayinezigidi eziyi-2.94, i-MSNBC yayinezigidi eziyi-2.89 ne-CNN yayinezigidi eziyi-2.52, utshilo uNilsen.
Emva kweentlanganiso, umdla wahlala uphezulu.
UFlake wayengumntu ophambili kwidrama yangoLwesihlanu.
Emva kokuba iofisi yamaRiphabliki alinganiselweyo ikhuphe ingxelo yokuba uza kuvuma uKavanaugh, wabanjwa kwiikhamera zeCNN neCBS ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni ekhwazwa ngabaqhankqalazi njengoko wayezama ukukhwela ikheshi ukuya kwintetho yeKomiti yoLungiso-mthetho.
Wema ebukhali kangangemizuzu emininzi njengoko wayethukwa, ethelekiswa ngqo kwiTV yeCNN.
Elinye ibhinqa lathi: "Ndihleli phambi kwakho".
"Ngaba ucinga ukuba uxelela ilizwe lakhe inyaniso?
Waxelelwa oku, "unamandla xa abafazi abaninzi bengenawo amandla".
UFlake wathi iofisi yakhe ikhuphe ingxelo yaye yathi, ngaphambi kokuba i-elevator ivalwe, uza kuba nokuninzi akuthethayo kwintlanganiso yekomiti.
Iinkqubo ze-cable nezocwangciso-ndaba zazisasaza zonke iiyure kamva, xa iKomiti yoLungiso-mthetho yayiza kuvota ukuze iqhube ukonyulwa kukaKavanaugh kwiSenate epheleleyo ukuze kuxoxwe ngayo.
Kodwa uFlake wathi uza kukwenza oko kuphela ngokuqonda ukuba iFBI iza kuhlolisisa izityholo ezibhekiswe kumntu ozonyulwe kwiveki ezayo, nto leyo ebikhuthazwa ngamaDemocrats angaphantsi.
UFlake wancedwa yinxalenye yincoko nomhlobo wakhe, uSen. uChris Coons.
Emva kwengxoxo noCoons kunye neSenators emva koko, uFlake wenza isigqibo sakhe.
Ukhetho lukaFlake lwalunamandla, kuba kwakubonakala ukuba amaRiphabliki awayi kuba namavoti okuvuma uKavanaugh ngaphandle kophando.
UMongameli Trump uvule uphando lweFBI malunga nezityholo ezenziwa nguKavanaugh.
UMongameli waseBritani uMay utyhola abagxeki 'bokuba badlala ezopolitiko' ngenxa yeBrexit
UMongameli Theresa May watyhola abagxeki bakhe ngezicwangciso zakhe zokumka kwi-European Union ngokuthi "badlala ezopolitiko" ngekamva laseBritani kwaye bephazamisa umdla wesizwe kudliwanondlebe nephephandaba iSunday Times.
INkulumbuso yaseBritani uTheresa May ifika kwiNgqungquthela yeConservative Party eBirmingham, eBritani, ngoSeptemba 29, 2018.
Kwenye ingxoxo ecaleni kweyaye yayikwiphepha lokuqala lephephandaba, owayengumphathiswa wezangaphandle uBoris Johnson wagxininisa ukuhlaselwa kwakhe kwesi sicwangciso sakhe seChequers seBrexit, esithi isindululo sokuba iBritani ne-EU kufuneka ziqokelele irhafu yomnye nomnye "siyinto engenangqiqo ngokupheleleyo".
Ukudubula kukaWayde Sims: Amapolisa abamba umtyholwa uDyteon Simpson ngokufa komdlali weLSU
Amapolisa abambe umntu osolwayo ngokubulawa ngokubulawa nguWayde Sims, umdlali webhola ekhatywayo oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala kwiLSU.
UDyteon Simpson, oneminyaka engama-20, ubanjwe waza wavalelwa entolongweni ngenxa yokubulala ngesigqibo sesibini, utshilo iSebe Lamapolisa laseBaton Rouge.
Amagosa asasaze ividiyo yokumelana kukaSims noSims, yaye amapolisa athi uSims walahlekelwa ziiglasi zakhe ebudeni bemfazwe.
Amapolisa afumana iiglasi kwindawo eyayenzekile aza athi afumene iDNA kaSimpson kuzo, ingxelo ye-CBS.
Emva kokuphonononga uSimpson, amapolisa athi wavuma ukuba wadubulana noWayde.
Ibhondi yakhe ibekwe kwi-350,000 yeedola, ingxelo yeGqwetha.
Iofisi yeCandelo loMngcwabo kwiParish yaseEast Baton Rouge yakhupha ingxelo yokuqala ngoLwesihlanu, isithi isizathu sokufa sisifo esenziwe ngompu entloko nasentanyeni.
Isebe libulela iqela elilawula abaphambukeli kwipholisa laseLouisiana, ilabhu yolwaphulo-mthetho, amapolisa aseYunivesithi yaseMzantsi nabemi bommandla ngokunceda kuphando olukhokelela ekubanjweni.
Umlawuli wezemidlalo weLSU uJoe Alleva wabulela amagosa omthetho kuloo mmandla "ngokukhuthala kwawo nokulandela ubulungisa".
USims wayeneminyaka engama-20 ubudala.
Lo mdlali uphakamileyo weenyawo ezi-6 wakhulela eBaton Rouge, apho uyise, uWayne, naye wadlala ibhola ekhatywayo kwiLSU.
Wenza umlinganiselo wamaphuzu ayi-5.6 kunye nama-2.6 ama-rebounds ngomdlalo kulo nyaka uphelileyo.
Ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, umqeqeshi webhola ekhatywayo weLSU uWill Wade wathi iqela "libhujisiwe" yaye "likhwankqisiwe" kukufa kukaWayde.
UWade wathi: "Yiloo nto usoloko ukhathazekile ngayo".
Intaba-mlilo ikhupha umlotha kwisiXeko saseMexico
Umlotha ovela kwintaba-mlilo iPopocatepetl uye wafikelela kumaphondo asemazantsi kwikomkhulu laseMexico.
IZiko leZizwe lokuThintelwa kweNtlekele lalumkisa abantu baseMexico ngoMgqibelo ukuba bahlale kude nentaba-mlilo emva kokuba umsebenzi uqalile kwintsimi yaye labhala imveliso yegesi nomlotha ongama-183 kwiiyure ezingama-24.
Iziko lalinolwazi ngeengxolo ezininzi nezinyikima.
Imifanekiso kwii-social media ibonisa iiglasi ezimfutshane zeemoto eziqweqwedisa umlotha kwiindawo ezikufutshane nesiXeko saseMexico ezinjengeXochimilco.
Oososayensi behlabathi baye baphawula ukunyuka komsebenzi kule ntaba-mlilo ikumgama weekhilomitha ezingama - 72 kumazantsi mpuma kwikomkhulu ukususela oko inyikima enkulu eyayinezikhukula ezenzekela imimandla eyi - 7.1 yazamazamisa kumbindi weMexico ngoSeptemba 2017.
Le ntaba-mlilo yaziwa ngokuba yi "Don Goyo" ibisebenza ukususela ngo-1994.
Amapolisa adibana nama-separatists aseCatalan ngaphambi komnyhadala wokuvota ngenkululeko
Abantu abathandathu babanjwa eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo emva kokuba ababhikishi abaxhasa ukuzimela bequbisane namapolisa okuphelisa uqhushululu, yaye njengoko amawaka ayejoyina imiboniso yokumelwa komnyaka wokuqala wokuvota kweCatalonia ngokuzimela.
Iqela lamajoni ahlukeneyo awayefihlakeleyo awabanjwe ngamapolisa okuphelisa uqhushululu labagxotha ngamaqanda laza laphosa upende olungumgubo, nto leyo eyenza ukuba kubekho amafu amnyama othuthu ezitratweni awayedla ngokuzaliswa ziindwendwe.
Kwakhona kwaqhambuka ukuxabana kamva ngemini apho amapolisa asebenzisa iintonga zawo ukuze athintele umlo.
Kangangeeyure ezininzi amaqela axhasa ukuzimela adanduluka esithi "Akukho ukulibala, akukho kuxolela" ajongana nababhikishi bamaqumrhu abathi, "Longe Spain".
Iindaba zasekuhlaleni zithi abantu abali-14 baye banyangwa ngenxa yokwenzakala okuncinane abafumanayo kwiimbambano.
Iingxabano zisaqhubeka ziphakame kummandla onqwenela ukuzimela unyaka emva kokuba iReferendum ka-Oktobha 1 ibonwa njengengavumelekanga eMadrid kodwa ibhiyozelwa ngamaCatalan ahlukeneyo.
Abavoti bakhetha ngokucacileyo ukuba babe ngabona bazizimeleyo, nangona abantu abachasene nokuhlukana ngokufuthi babhokota.
Ngokutsho kwamagunya aseCatalan phantse abantu abayi-1 000 balimala kunyaka ophelileyo emva kokuba amapolisa ezama ukuyeka ukuvota kwiindawo zokhetho kulo lonke elo mmandla kwiingxabano ezinogonyamelo.
Amaqela axhasa ukuzimela aye akhawuleze ebusuku ngoLwesihlanu ukuze athintele umbhikisho wokuxhasa amapolisa asekuhlaleni.
Lo mboniso waqhubeka kodwa wanyanzelwa ukuba athathe indlela eyahlukileyo.
UNarcis Termes, oneminyaka engama-68, ugesi owayesenza imiboniso yokwahlukana nomfazi wakhe wathi akasathembanga ukuba iCatalonia iza kuba nelizwe elizimeleyo.
"Ngo nyaka ophelileyo safumana enye yeyona mizuzu yethu mihle.
Ndabona abazali bam bekhala ngovuyo kuba bekwazi ukuvota kodwa ngoku siphazamisekile", utshilo.
Nangona bephumelele ngempumelelo ebalulekileyo nangona incinane kunyulo lweengingqi ngoDisemba ophelileyo, amaqela aseCatalan alwela ukuzimela aye alwela ukugcina amandla kulo nyaka, kunye neenkokeli zawo ezininzi ezaziwayo nokuba zisebuphambukweni okanye ziboshwe zilindele ityala ngenxa yendima yazo ekuququzeleleni irefendum kunye nokuvakaliswa kwenkululeko okulandelayo.
UJoan Puig, umenzi-mveliso oneminyaka engama-42 ubudala, owenza irekhodi leemviwo zokubonisa inkxaso yamapolisa kwifowuni yakhe, uthi le ngxabano iye yavuselelwa ngabezopolitiko kumacala omabini.
Wathi: "Kusiya kusiba nzima ngakumbi".
NgoMgqibelo, uOriol Junqueras, omnye weenkokeli ezisithoba zaseCatalan ezisejele ukususela ekupheleni konyaka ophelileyo, wabhengeza ukuba uza kulinda ukhetho lwePalamente yaseYurophu kunyaka ozayo.
"Ukuziphakamisa njengombonisi kunyulo lwaseYurophu yeyona ndlela ilungileyo yokugxeka ukubuyela umva kwamanani entando yesininzi kunye nokugxekwa esiye sabona kukarhulumente waseSpeyin", utshilo.
