Ukuphazamiseka kwaqhambuka kwi-HMP Long Lartin eWorcestershire malunga ne-9:30 BST ngeCawa kwaye kuyaqhubeka.
Amagosa agqwesileyo "eTornado" aye aziswa ukuze ajongane nale ngxokozelo, ebandakanya amabanjwa asibhozo yaye ikwiphiko elinye.
La mapolisa ayegonywa ngenxa yokwenzakala kobuso obulula kwindawo eyayenzeke le nto.
Isithethi seNkonzo yeeNtolongo sathi: "Abasebenzi basezintolongweni abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo baye bathunyelwa ukuze bajongane nesiganeko esiqhubekayo kwiHMP Long Lartin.
Amalungu amathandathu abasebenzi aye anyangwa ngenxa yokwenzakala.
Asiyinyamezeli ingcinezelo kwiinkampu zethu zentolongo, yaye siyaqonda ukuba abo banembopheleleko baya kuthunyelwa emapoliseni baze bachithe ixesha elide emva kwezikhonkwane".
IMP Long Lartin ibambe amabanjwa angaphezu kwama-500, kuquka amanye amabanjwa anobungozi kwilizwe.
