Inkanyamba URosa Isongela iPhoenix, eLas Vegas, eSalt Lake City Ngezikhukula (Iindawo Ezomileyo Zinokuzuza)
Kunqabile ukuba i-tropical depression ihlasele iArizona, kodwa oko kanye kusenokwenzeka ukuba kwenzeke ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo njengoko inkanyamba uRosa isasaza amandla aseleyo entlango esemazantsi ntshona, nto leyo ebangela ukuba kubekho izikhukula.
I-National Weather Service sele ikhuphe iiyure zokuza kwezikhukula ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini kwintshona yeArizona ukuya kumzantsi nasempuma yeNevada, kumazantsi mpuma eCalifornia naseUtah, kuquka izixeko zasePhoenix, eFlagstaff, eLas Vegas naseSalt Lake City.
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa athabathe indlela ethe ngqo phezu kweFenix ngoLwesibini, esondela emva kwexesha ngoMvulo ngemvula.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix yathi kwi-tweet yayo "kwiinkanyamba ezilishumi kuphela ezitshitshisayo ezikhusele imeko yeenkanyamba ezitshisayo okanye ezitshutshisayo ngaphakathi kweekhilomitha ezingama-200 ukusuka ePhoenix ukususela ngowe-1950!
UKatrina (1967) yayingumkhukula ongaphantsi kweekhilomitha ezingama-40 ukusuka kumda weAZ".
Iimodeli zakutshanje zeNational Hurricane Center zixela imvula engama - 2 ukuya kuma - 4 intshi, kunye nemitha eyahlukileyo ukuya kuma - 6 intshi eMogollon Rim yaseArizona.
Ezinye iindawo eziseMzantsi-ntshona weNtlango kuquka iRocky Mountains esezantsi kunye neGreat Basin kusenokwenzeka ukuba zifikelele kwi-1 ukuya kwi-2 intshi, kunye nezibalo ezizodwa ukuya kwi-4 intshi.
Kulabo basengozini yokukhukula ngokukhawuleza, imvula yaseRosa isenokuba yintsikelelo kuba lo mmandla usongelwe yimbalela.
Nangona izikhukula ziyinkxalabo enkulu, kusenokwenzeka ukuba ezinye zezi mvula ziya kuba luncedo ekubeni uMzantsi-ntshona ngoku uneemeko ezomileyo.
Ngokutsho kweU.S. Drought Monitor, ngaphezu nje kwe-40 pesenti yeArizona inengxaki yokunqongophala kwamanzi, ibe le yeyona ndawo iphambili", yatsho i-weather.com.
Okokuqala, indlela yeNkanyamba uRosa ikhokelela ekungeneni kwamanzi kwiNhlonhlo yaseBaja California eMexico.
URosa, osenamandla okwenza isiphepho ngeCawa ekuseni, eneemitha ezingama - 85 ngeyure, usema - 385 miles kumzantsi wePunta Eugenia, eMexico yaye uhamba umgama ongezantsi ngeemayile ezili - 12 ngeyure.
Le nkanyamba idibana namanzi abandayo kwiPasifiki yaye ngenxa yoko iyacima amandla.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba ifike eMexico ngamandla esorha eshushu emini okanye ngokuhlwa yangoMvulo.
Imvula enetha kwiindawo ezithile zaseMexico isenokuba namandla, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba kubekho izikhukula.
I-weather.com yathi: "Kulindelwe imvula engange-3 ukuya kwee-intshi ezisi-6 ukusuka eBaa California ukuya kumntla-ntshona weSonora, ize ifike kwii-intshi ezili-10".
URosa uza kulandela emantla eMexico njengesaqhwithi esishushu ngaphambi kokuba afikelele kumda waseArizona ngentsasa yokuqala ngoLwesibini njengesifo esishushu, esiya kuthi emva koko sihambe ngeArizona siye kumazantsi eUtah ngasekupheleni kobusuku ngoLwesibini.
IZiko Lehlabathi Leenkanyamba lithi: "Eyona ngozi ilindelekileyo kwiRosa okanye kwintsalela yayo yimvula enzulu kakhulu eBaa California, kumntla-ntshona weSonora, nakummandla waseMzantsi-ntshona weNtlango yaseMerika".
Kulindeleke ukuba ezi mvula zibangele izikhukula ezibulalayo, imingxuma ihambe entlango, yaye iindiza zikhukhule kwiindawo ezintabeni.
