UTrump uthi uKavanaugh 'wabandezeleka, ubundlobongela, umsindo' weqela lamaDemokhrasi
"Ukuvota kwiJaji Kavanaugh kukuvota ukwala iqhinga elingenanceba nelidumileyo leqela lamaDemokhrasi", utshilo uTrump kwindibano eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia.
UTrump uthe uKavanaugh "wabandezeleka kukuxhatshazwa, ngumsindo" weqela lamaDemocratic Party kuyo yonke inkqubo yakhe yokumiswa.
UKavanaugh wafakaza phambi kweCongress ngoLwesine, engazange avume ngamandla nangokweemvakalelo ukuba uChristine Blasey Ford uthi wamxhaphaza ngokwesondo kumashumi eminyaka eyadlulayo xa babeselula.
UFord naye wavuma phambi kweentlanganiso malunga nezityholo zakhe.
UMongameli wathi ngoMgqibelo "abantu baseMerika babona ubuchule, umgangatho nesibindi" sikaKavanaugh ngaloo mini.
"Ivoti yokuqinisekisa uMgwebi Kavanaugh livoti yokuqinisekisa omnye weengqondo zomthetho eziphumeleleyo zexesha lethu, ummeli onembali entle kwinkonzo karhulumente", watsho kwisihlwele esisekelwa yiWest Virginia.
UMongameli wabhekisela ngokungazenzisiyo kunyulo lukaKavanaugh ngelixa ethetha ngokubaluleka kokuthatha inxaxheba kwamaRiphabliki kunyulo lwexesha eliphakathi.
"Kusele iiveki ezintlanu ngaphambi kokubakho kolunye lolona khetho lubalulekileyo ebomini bethu.
Andibaleki, kodwa ndibaleka ngokwenene", watsho.
"Kungenxa yoko le nto ndihlala ndixhaphaza abantu ababalaseleyo".
UTrump wathi amaDemocrat anesabelo "sokuxhathisa nokuthintelwa".
Ukuvotelwa kokuqala okuphambili kwenkqubo kwiSenate floor malunga nokumiselwa kukaKavanaugh kulindeleke ukuba kwenzeke kungekudala ngoLwesihlanu, umncedisi ophezulu wokukhokela we-GOP uxelele i-CNN.
Amakhulu abulawa yinyikima, itsunami eIndonesia, yaye inani labantu ababuleweyo liye landa
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 babulawa, abaninzi batshitshiswa ngamaza amakhulu abetha iilwandle, xa inyikima enkulu kunye netsunami zithe zabetha isiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi, zatsho izikhulu ngoMgqibelo.
Ngolwesihlanu amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene ukuze adle ibhiyozo elunxwemeni kwisixeko sasePalu xa amaza aphakamileyo kangangemitha ezintandathu (18 yeenyawo) awela elunxwemeni xa kwakuhlwa, esusa abaninzi de bafa yaye esitshabalalisa nantoni na eyayisendleleni yabo.
Itsunami yalandelwa yinyikima yomhlaba enamandla angama-7.5.
"Xa kwabakho isoyikiso se-tsunami izolo, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo elunxwemeni yaye abazange babaleke ngoko nangoko baza baba ngamaxhoba", utshilo uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-arhente yaseIndonesia yokunciphisa iintlekele i-BNPB kwintlanganiso eJakarta.
UNugroho uthi: "Itsunami ayizange ivele ngokwayo, yahlutha iimoto, imithi, izindlu, yabetha yonke into esemhlabeni", yaye wongezelela ukuba le tsunami yayihamba ngaphaya kolwandle ngesantya esifikelela kwiikhilomitha ezingama-800 ngeyure ngaphambi kokuba iwele kunxweme.
Wathi abanye abantu bakhuphuka emithini ukuze baphephe i-tsunami baza basinda.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16,700 bahamba baya kwiindawo ezingama-24 ePalu.
Imifanekiso evela emoyeni ekhutshwe liziko leentlekele ibonisa izakhiwo ezininzi neeveki ezibhidliweyo, amabhulorho agqobhozayo yaye ewile nomzi womzi.
Ukuzamazama kwasemva kwaqhubeka kushukunyisa isixeko esiselunxwemeni ngoMgqibelo.
Olu ngcelele lweenyikima zaziva kwindawo enabantu abazizigidi ezingama - 2.4
I-Indeonesia's Agency for the Assessment and Application of Technology (BPPT) yathi kwingxelo yayo amandla akhutshwa yinyikima enkulu yangoLwesihlanu ayimalunga nama-200 amandla ombane weathom owaphoswa eHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ithi, indawo yesixeko, esikwindawo ende, encinane, isenokuba yandisa ubungakanani beetsunami.
UNugroho wachaza umonakalo ngokuthi "ngumkhulu" waza wathi amawaka ezindlu, izibhedlele, iindawo zokuthenga neehotele zabhidlika.
Iidumbu zabanye abantu ababethwa zifunyenwe zibanjwe phantsi kweenkunkuma zezakhiwo eziwileyo, uthe, wongezelela wathi abantu abangama-540 balimele yaye abangama-29 abekho.
UNugroho uthe amaxhoba kunye nomonakalo unokuba mkhulu kunalo lonke unxweme olukho kwiikhilomitha ezingama-300 ngasentla kwePalu, indawo ebizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, esondele kwincopho yenyikima.
UNugroho wathi, "ukunxibelelana kwakuphazamisekile ngokupheleleyo ngaphandle kolwazi" oluvela eDonggala.
