UJohn Edward: Izakhono zolwimi ezibalulekileyo kubemi behlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zigcina irekhodi lokuqhuba kakuhle kwezemfundo, kwaye oku kuqhubeke ngo-2018 ngeseti enye yeziphumo ezibalaseleyo zeemvavanyo, ezomelezwa kuphela yimpumelelo yomntu ngamnye kunye nehlanganisiweyo kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo kunye neminye imizamo yoluntu.
Ngaphezulu kwabantwana abangama-30,000 eScotland, ezi zikolo, zimelwe yiBhunga laseScotland leZikolo ezizimeleyo (SCIS), zizama ukubonelela ngeyona nqanaba liphezulu lenkonzo kubafundi babo nakubazali.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zijolise ekulungiseleleni abafundi bazo kwimfundo ephakamileyo, umsebenzi abawukhethileyo kunye nendawo yabo njengabahlali behlabathi.
Njengomhlaba wemfundo onokwakha nokusebenzisa inkqubo yesikolo esenzelwe wena, sibona iilwimi zanamhlanje ziqhubeka zifana nesifundo esithandwayo nesithandwayo ezikolweni.
UNelson Mandela wathi: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi alwaziyo, loo nto iya entloko yakhe.
Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe, uya kuyiqonda intliziyo yakhe".
Esi sisikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuba asinakuxhomekeka kwisiNgesi xa sifuna ukwakha ubudlelwane nokuthembela nabantu abavela kwamanye amazwe.
Kwiziphumo zovavanyo zonyaka zakutshanje, sibona ukuba iilwimi ziphambili kwiitheyibhile zezikolo ezizimeleyo ezinamanani aphezulu okuphumelela.
I-68% yabafundi abafunda iilwimi zasemzini bafumene isidanga esiphezulu se-A.
Idatha, ehlanganiswe kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezingoolungu ze-SCIS, yabonisa ukuba i-72% yabafundi bafumene inqanaba eliphakamileyo le-A ngesiMandarin, ngelixa i-72% yabo bafunda isiJamani, i-69% yabo bafunda isiFrentshi kunye ne-63% yabo bafunda iSpanish nabo bafumene inqaku eli-A.
Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eSkotlani zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo eziya kufunwa ngabantwana nolutsha ngokuqinisekileyo kwixesha elizayo.
Iilwimi ngoku, njengento ekhethwayo, zenziwa ngendlela efanayo nezifundo ze-STEM (inzululwazi, iteknoloji, ubunjineli kunye nemathematika) kwizifundo ezikolweni ezizimeleyo nakwezinye iindawo.
