Ngoko ke, ulwimi luye lwaba yinto ebalulekileyo ukuze ulutsha lungene kumsebenzi oluzayo.
Ngenxa yokuba amathuba emisebenzi engakumbi afuna iilwimi, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi eliguquguqukayo.
Enoba umntu ukhetha yiphi na umsebenzi, ukuba ufunde ulwimi lwesibini, uya kuba nenzuzo yokwenene kwixesha elizayo yokuba nobuchule obuhlala buhleli.
Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngokuthe ngqo nabantu abavela kumazwe asemzini kuya kubeka umntu othetha iilwimi ezininzi phambi komntu okhuphisana naye.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwe yi-YouGov kubantu abadala base-UK abangaphezu kwe-4 000 ngo-2013, ama-75 ekhulwini ayengazi kuthetha ulwimi lwasemzini ngokwaneleyo ukuba akwazi ukuqhuba incoko kwaye isiFrentshi sisona silwimi kuphela esithethwa ngamaphesenti anamanani amabini, i-15%.
Kungenxa yoko le nto ukutyala imali ngoku ekufundiseni ulwimi kubalulekile kubantwana banamhlanje.
Ukuba neelwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zezoqoqosho ezikhulayo, kuya kunceda abantwana babe nethuba elingakumbi lokufumana umsebenzi onentsingiselo.
EScotland, isikolo ngasinye siya kwahluka ngeelwimi esizifundisayo.
Ezinye izikolo ziya kugxila kwiilwimi zakudala, ngelixa ezinye ziya kufundisa iilwimi ezijongwa njengezona zibalulekileyo e-UK xa ujonge phambili kwi-2020, ezinje ngeMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Enoba umntwana wakho unomdla kangakanani na, uya kuhlala ekwazi ukukhetha iilwimi ezininzi ezikolweni ezizimeleyo, apho kukho ootitshala abaqeqeshiweyo abaqeqeshiweyo kule nkalo.
Izikolo zaseScotland ezizimeleyo zinikezelwe ekuboneleleni ngendawo yokufunda eya kulungiselela abantwana baze babaxhobise ngezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele, kungakhathaliseki ukuba yintoni ikamva eliya kubaphathela yona.
Akunakuphikwa okwangoku, kwimozulu yeshishini yehlabathi, ukuba iilwimi ziyaqhubeka zibaluleke kakhulu kwikamva lelizwe, ngoko oku kufuneka kubonakaliswe kwimfundo.
