UMongameli uDonald Trump uqala umkhosi wemibutho yokunyusa abantu namhlanje eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia.
Le yeyokugqibela kwiindibano ezintlanu zikaTrump ezicwangciselwe iveki ezayo, kuquka ukuza kuma kwindawo ezinobuhlobo kuquka iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngoxa ukuvotelwa kwakhe ukuqinisekisa ukuba uza kugcwalisa isithuba esivulekileyo kwiNkundla ePhakamileyo, uTrump ujonge ukwakha inkxaso kunyulo oluzayo lwexesha eliphakathi kuba amaRiphabliki asengozini yokuphulukana nolawulo lweCongress xa kuvunywa ngevoti ngoNovemba.
Liliphi ixesha eliza kuba semva kweMbhikisho kaTrump eNtshona Virginia namhlanje yaye ubukela njani kwi-intanethi?
Umsitho kaTrump waseWheeling, eNtshona Virginia ucwangciselwe ukuza ngo-7:00 ebusuku ebusuku ngoLwesibini, ngoSeptemba 29, 2018.
Unokuyibukela i-Rally kaTrump eNtshona Virginia kwi-intanethi ngezantsi nge-YouTube.
USomashishini kaTrump kusenokwenzeka ukuba uza kuthetha kule veki kwiingxoxo zokumangalelwa kukaBrett Kavanaugh weNkundla Ephakamileyo, owaba ngoxanduva lwezityholo zokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesondo, njengoko kwakulindeleke ukuba kuvotelwe ukuqinisekiswa kweSenate kuze kube liveki elinye ngelixa iFBI iphengulula.
Kodwa injongo ephambili yale ntlanganiso kukunceda amaRiphabliki ajongene nolonyulo lukaNovemba afumane inkqubela.
Ngaloo ndlela, iphulo likaMongameli Trump lathi ezi ntlanganiso zintlanu kwiveki ezayo zijolise "ekukhuthazeni amavolontiya kunye nabalandeli njengoko amaRiphabliki ezama ukukhusela nokwandisa ubukhulu bawo kwiSenate naseNdlwini yaBameli", ngokutsho kweReuters.
"Ulawulo lweCongress lubaluleke kakhulu kwi-ajenda yakhe kangangokuba umongameli uza kuhamba aye kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko kunokwenzeka njengoko sifika kwixesha elinomtsalane lokunyusa", utshilo isithethi somkhankaso kaTrump esala ukubizwa ngegama kuReuters.
I-Wesbanco Arena eWheeling, iya kuba nomngcelele wabancedi abavela eOhio nasePennsylvania, yaye iza kuba neendaba ezivela kwiindaba zasePittsburgh, ngokutsho kweWest Virginia Metro News.
NgoMgqibelo kuya kuba lixesha lesibini kule nyanga idlulileyo uTrump etyelele iNtshona Virginia, ilizwe awalinqoba ngamaphuzu angaphezu kwama-40 ekhulwini ngo-2016.
UTrump uzama ukunceda umviwa weSenate waseWest Virginia ongumRepublican uPatrick Morrisey, obambelela emva kwevoti.
USimon Haeder, isazi ngezepolitiki kwiYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, uthi: "Asikho isibonakaliso esihle sokuba uMorrisey kufuneka eze kumongameli ukuze azame ukumnika inkxaso kwiinyulo".
