UMzantsi Korea uthi 'akukho ndlela' eya kuhlutha izixhobo ngaphandle kokuthembela
Umphathiswa wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iZizwe eziManyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba ukuqhubeka kwezo zithintelo kuqinisa ukungathembani kwayo neUnited States kwaye akukho ndlela yokuba ilizwe lilahle izixhobo zalo zenyukliya ngokwahlukileyo phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo.
URi Yong Ho uxelele iNdibano Jikelele yonyaka yequmrhu lehlabathi ukuba uMntla Korea uthathe "amanyathelo abalulekileyo okwenza izinto ezilungileyo" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanywa kweenyukliya neendubane, ukuchitha indawo yokuvavanywa kwenyukliya, nokuzibophelela ekubeni ingayi kusasaza izixhobo zenyukliya nobuchwepheshe benyukliya.
Wathi: "Nangona kunjalo, asiboni mpendulo ifanelekileyo evela eUnited States".
"Ngaphandle kokuthembela eUnited States, akuyi kubakho kuthembela kukhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe yaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo akukho ndlela yokuba singazixhophazi ngokuthe ngqo kuqala".
Nangona uRi ephinda izikhalazo eziqhelekileyo zaseNyakatho Korea malunga nokuxhathisa kweWashington kwindlela "enamanqanaba" yokulwa ne-denuclearization apho iNyakatho Korea yayiya kuvuzwa njengoko ithatha amanyathelo ngokuthe ngcembe, ingxelo yakhe yabonakala ibalulekile kuba ayizange ikulahle ngokulula ukulwa ne-denuclearization njengePyongyang eyenzile ngaphambili.
URi wabhekisela kwingxelo edibeneyo eyenziwe nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwintlanganiso yokuqala phakathi komongameli wase-US kunye nenkokeli yaseMntla Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12, xa uKim wathembisa ukusebenza "ukungabi namathumba kwintshona yeKorea" ngelixa uTrump wathembisa ukuqinisekisa ukhuseleko lwaseMntla Korea.
I-North Korea iye yafuna ukuphela ngokusemthethweni kweMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States ithi iPyongyang kufuneka iqale ilahle izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington iphinde yachasana nezicelo zokunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezibekwe uMntla Korea.
"I-US igxininisa "ekunciphiseni izixhobo zenyukliya kuqala" kwaye inyusa inqanaba loxinzelelo lwezibheno ukuze zifezekise injongo yazo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, kwaye ikwala "ukubhengeza ukuphela kwemfazwe", "utshilo uRi.
"Ingcamango yokuba izigwebo zinokusenza siguquke iphupha labantu abangenalo ulwazi ngathi.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba ukuqhubeka kwezi zithintelo kuyenza ingathembani ngakumbi".
URi akazange athethe ngezicwangciso zeengqungquthela zesibini phakathi kukaKim noTrump, ezenziwa yinkokeli yaseMerika kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kweveki.
Kunoko, lo mphathiswa wabhekisela kwiintlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim nenkokeli yaseMzantsi Korea uMun Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo waza wongezelela wathi: "Ukuba uMzantsi Korea wawungekho kwilizwe laseMerika, ukuhluthwa kweenqwelo-moya ezisemhlabeni kwakungayi kufika kwindawo engenazimpawu".
Nangona kunjalo, ithoni yentetho kaRi yahluke kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo, xa waxelela i-UN General Assembly ukuba ukujolisa kwilizwe laseMerika ngeentolo zaseMntla Korea kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba "uMongameli uMnu Evil" Trump ebize uKim ngokuthi "ngumntu weentolo" kwimisebenzi yokuzibulala.
Kulo nyaka kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo, uTrump, owathi kunyaka ophelileyo "uzakuyichitha ngokupheleleyo" iNyakatho Korea, wadumisa uKim ngesibindi sakhe ekuthatheni amanyathelo okucima izixhobo, kodwa wathi kusekuninzi okusamele kwenziwe kwaye kufuneka kuqhubeke nezigwebo de iNyakatho Korea ingabi namathumba.
NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathi akanalo ixesha lokuyenza le nto, esithi "Ukuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu - akunamsebenzi".
I-China neRashiya zithi iBhunga loKhuseleko le-UN kufuneka livuze iPyongyang ngamanyathelo athathweyo.
Noko ke, uNobhala Wezangaphandle waseMerika uMike Pompeo wathi kwiBhunga Lezokhuseleko leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoLwesine: "Ukunyanzeliswa kwezo zithintelo zeBhunga Lezokhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngamandla yaye ngaphandle kokuphoswa de sifezekise ukuphelelwa zixhobo zenyukliya ngokupheleleyo, ekugqibeleni nokuqinisekisiweyo".
ISigqeba seZigqeba zoKhuseleko siye saqinisa izigwebo ezibekwe uMntla Korea ukususela ngo-2006 ukuze siphephe imali yeprogram yePyongyang yenyukliya neentsholongwane.
UPompeo wadibana noRi ecaleni kweNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo waza wathi emva koko uza kuphinda atyelele iPyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukuze alungiselele intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo uye watyelela eMntla Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugqibela aluzange luphumelele kakuhle.
Washiya iPyongyang ngoJulayi esithi sele yenziwe inkqubela, kodwa emva kweeyure nje ezimbalwa uMntla Korea wamtyhola ngokwenza "iimfuno ezinjengezigebenga".
UMntla Korea uthembise kwintlanganiso kunye noMnu kule nyanga ukuba uza kucima indawo yezikhali-mkhosi kunye neenkqubo zenyukliya ukuba iUnited States ithatha "amanyathelo afanelekileyo".
Uthi uKim wamxelela ukuba "amanyathelo afanelekileyo" awayefuna ukuba afumane wona ziziqinisekiso zokhuseleko ezathenjiswa nguTrump eSingapore kwaye uhamba ukuya kuzinzisa ubudlelwane neWashington.
Abafundi baseHarvard bafunda ukuphumla ngokwaneleyo
Ikhosi entsha kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard kulo nyaka iye yabangela ukuba bonke abafundi bayo bafumane ubuthongo obuninzi ukuze balwe nenkcubeko ekhulayo yama-macho yokufunda 'ngobusuku bonke' enikwe i-caffeine.
Omnye umphengululi wafumanisa ukuba abafundi baseyunivesithi yokuqala ehlabathini badla ngokungazi ukuba bafanele baziphathe njani.
UCharles Czeisler, onguprofesa wezokwelapha zokulala kwiSikolo saseHarvard seZonyango kunye nengcali kwiBrigham and Women's Hospital, wayila le khosi, ekholelwa ukuba yeyokuqala kolu hlobo eUnited States.
Waphefumlelwa ukuba aqalise isifundo emva kokuba enikele intetho ebonisa indlela ukungalali kakuhle okwakuchaphazela ngayo ukufunda.
'Emva kokuba ndigqibile, enye intombazana yeza kum yaza yathi: 'Kutheni ndixelelwa oku nje ngoku, kunyaka wam wokugqibela?'
Wathi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ngokubaluleka kokulala - nto leyo yandothusa,' watsho kwiThe Telegraph.
Esi sikolo, esiqalisiwe okokuqala kulo nyaka, sichaza abafundi izinto ezibalulekileyo ngendlela ukulala kakuhle okunokubanceda ngayo abafundi baphumelele kwezemfundo nakwimidlalo, kwakunye nokuphucula impilo yabo ngokubanzi.
UPaul Barreira, onguprofesa wezifo zengqondo kwiHarvard Medical School nomlawuli olawulayo weenkonzo zempilo zeyunivesithi, uthi eyunivesithi yagqiba kwelokuba isungule le khosi emva kokufumanisa ukuba abafundi babengenalo ixesha lokulala ebudeni beveki.
Iklasi yeeyure eziliqela iquka uthotho lwemisebenzi enxibelelanayo.
Kwelinye icandelo kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokuhlala, apho abafundi becofa kwiikomityi zekofu, kwizikrini, kwizikhupheli nakwiincwadi ukuze baxelelwe ngeempembelelo zecaffeine nokukhanya nendlela ukusebenza kwezemidlalo okuchaphazeleka ngayo kukungalali ngokwaneleyo, nokubaluleka komsebenzi wokulala.
Kwelinye icandelo, abathathi-nxaxheba baxelelwa indlela ukungalali ixesha elide okunokubandisa ngayo umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa sisifo sentliziyo, ukubetha, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Imephu yekhampasi, eneempawu ezisebenza ngokudibana, ikhuthaza abathathi-nxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngemisebenzi yabo yemihla ngemihla.
'Siyazi ukuba akuyi kutshintsha indlela abaziphatha ngayo abafundi ngoko nangoko.
Kodwa sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokwazi - kanye njengokuba nawe unelungelo lokwazi imiphumo yempilo yokukhetha ukutshaya icuba,' wongezelela uGqr.
Wathi, inkcubeko yokuzingca 'ngokuhlala ubusuku bonke' isekho, yaye wongezelela ukuba ubugcisa bale mihla noxinzelelo oluhlala lukhula kubafundi lubangela ukuba ukungalali kube yingxaki ekhulayo.
Wathi ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulala ngokwaneleyo, umgangatho omhle, kufanele kube 'sisixhobo esifihlakeleyo' somfundi ekulweni noxinzelelo, ukudinwa nokuxhalaba - kwanokukuphepha ukongeza ubunzima, ekubeni ukungalali kubeka ingqondo kwimodi yokulamba, nto leyo eyenza ihlale ilambile.
