Abameli bamazwe ali-18 kunye nesiphaluka bafake ingxelo yomhlobo wenkundla ngoLwesihlanu eWashington ukuze baxhase umenzi-sicelo ochasene nalo mgaqo-nkqubo, kubika i-NBC News.
