Umgaqo-nkqubo omtsha we-US wokuphepha-mvume wasusa isigqibo seBhodi yeZibheno zabafuduki ngowama-2014 esivumela abafuduki abangenamaxwebhu abaleka ugonyamelo lwasekhaya ukuba bafake isicelo sokuphepha-mvume.
