Amagqwetha aphinda athi umgaqo-nkqubo wokwala ukufudukela kwamanye amazwe uyonakalisa uqoqosho lwaseMerika, esithi banokuba ngoosomashishini baze "banike abantu abasebenza nzima".
Umtshutshisi Jikelele uJeff Sessions wayalela abagwebi abafudukela kwelinye ilizwe ukuba bangaphindi banikezele ngesigxina amaxhoba abaleka ukuxhatshazwa kwasekhaya nobundlobongela bamaxhoba ngoJuni.
USessions wathi kwisikhumbuzo sakhe esenziwa ngoJuni 11 somgaqo-nkqubo: "Ukusasazeka kuyafumaneka kwabo bashiya ilizwe labo ngenxa yentshutshiso okanye uloyiko ngenxa yohlanga, unqulo, ubuzwe, okanye ubulungu kwiqela elithile loluntu okanye imbono yezopolitiko".
Isiphephelo asizange senzelwe ukunciphisa zonke iingxaki - nkqu nazo zonke iingxaki ezinzulu - abantu abajamelana nazo yonke imihla ehlabathini lonke.
Imigudu yokunceda abantu ePalu iphantse yaphindaphindeka kabini njengoko abantu befuna abasindileyo
Kwabasindileyo, imeko yayisiya iba mbi ngakumbi nangakumbi.
"Kubuhlungu gqitha", watsho umama oneminyaka engama-35 ubudala uRisa Kusuma, ethuthuzela usana lwakhe olunefiva kwiziko lokufuduka kwidolophu ekhulayo yasePalu.
"Mzuzu ngamnye iambulensi izisa izidumbu.
Amanzi acocekileyo ayisiyonto".
Abemi babonwa bebuyela kumakhaya abo ayonakeleyo, beqokelela izinto ezimanzi, bezama ukuhlangula nantoni na abayifumanayo.
Amakhulu abantu alinyazwa yaye izibhedlele, ezonakaliswe yinyikima enamandla angama-7.5, zathinteka.
Abanye abalimali, kuquka uDwi Haris, owaphuka umqolo nomqolo, baphumla phandle kwesibhedlele somkhosi sasePalu, apho izigulana zazinyangwa ngaphandle ngenxa yokunyikima okuqhubekayo.
Iinyembezi zazigcwele amehlo akhe njengoko wayebalisa indlela awavakalelwa ngayo xa inyikima enkulu yayinyikima igumbi lakhe ehotele elisekumgangatho wesihlanu awayenalo nomfazi nentombi yakhe.
"Asakwazi ukuzikhusela.
Ndicinga ukuba ndaxinwa ndaya kumabhodlo odonga", watsho uHaris kwiAssociated Press, echaza ukuba intsapho yakhe yayisezixekweni ukuze ibe nomtshato.
"Ndasiva umfazi wam ekhala ecela uncedo, kodwa ke wathula.
Andazi ukuba kwenzeke ntoni kuye nakwimntwana wam.
Ndiyathemba ukuba baphilile".
Ummeli waseMerika utyhola iChina 'ngokuxhaphaza' 'ngeentengiso zentengiso'
Kwiveki emva kokuba iphephandaba laseTshayina elisemthethweni liye lapapasha isibhengezo samaphepha amane kwimihla ngemihla yaseMerika esibhengeza iingenelo ezifanayo zorhwebo lwaseMerika neTshayina, isithunywa saseMerika eChina sityhola iBeijing ngokusebenzisa amajelo eendaba aseMerika ukusasaza intetho.
UMongameli waseMerika uDonald Trump ngoLwesithathu ophelileyo wabhekisela kwisongezelelo esihlawulwayo seChina Daily kwiDes Moines Register - eyona phephandaba ithengisa kakhulu eIowa - emva kokumangalela iChina ngokuzama ukuphazamisa ukhetho lweCongress yaseMerika ngoNovemba 6, ityala eliphikiswa yiChina.
Isityholo sikaTrump sokuba iBeijing izama ukuphazamisa ukhetho lwaseMerika, sibonisa oko amagosa aseMerika athi iReuters sisigaba esitsha kumkhankaso owelayo waseWashington wokubeka uxinzelelo eChina.
Nangona kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe babeke iintengiso zokukhuthaza urhwebo, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zivalelwe kwimpikiswano yokurhweba ekhulayo eye yabangela ukuba zilinganise iindidi zemirhumo kwamanye amazwe.
Iirhafu zokuziphindezela zaseTshayina ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo zazenzelwe ukubetha abathengisi kumazwe afana neIowa abaxhasa iqela likaTrump lamaRiphabliki, iingcali zaseTshayina nezaseMerika zithi.
UTerry Branstad, ongummeli wase-US e-China nowayesakuba ngumlawuli wase-Iowa ixesha elide, owayengumthengisi omkhulu weempahla zezolimo e-China, wathi iBeijing iye yalimaza abasebenzi base-US, amafama namashishini.
UBranstad wabhala kwiphepha lakhe leendaba laseDes Moines Register ngeCawa, esithi iChina "ngoku iphindaphindeka kabini le mbambano ngokwenza iintengiso zentengiso kwiindaba zethu ezikhululekileyo".
UBranstad wabhala wathi: "Ukarhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa inkcubeko yaseMerika yenkululeko yokuthetha nenkululeko yeendaba ngokwenza intengiso ehlawulwayo kwiDes Moines Register".
Wabhala wathi: "Ngokwahlukileyo koko, kwibhodi yephephandaba esecaleni kwendlela apha eBeijing, uya kufumana amazwi angafaniyo ancinane yaye awuyi kubona nayiphi na imbono yokwenene yeembono ezahlukahlukeneyo ezinokuba nazo abantu baseTshayina ngendlela eyonakalisayo eqhubeka ngayo uqoqosho lwaseTshayina, ekubeni amajelo eendaba elawulwa ngamandla yiCawa yamaKomanisi yaseTshayina".
Wongezelela esithi "enye yephephandaba elidumileyo laseTshayina ayizange ifune ukupapasha" inqaku lakhe, nangona engazange athi yeyiphi.
AmaRiphabliki Athintela Abavoti Abafazi Ngaphambi Kwexesha Lokusetyenziswa Kwezikhundla ZamaNgqina KaYehova NgoKavanaugh Debacle, Abahlalutyi Balumkisa
Njengoko amaRiphabliki amaninzi aphezulu ehlala ekulungeleyo ukukhusela umviwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh xa eboniswa izityholo ezininzi zokuhlaselwa ngokwesondo, abahlalutyi balumkise ukuba baza kubona impendulo, ngokukodwa evela kumabhinqa, ngexesha lonyulo oluzayo.
Iimvakalelo ezijikeleze oku ziye zaba phezulu kakhulu, kwaye uninzi lwabaPhathiswa bamaRiphabliki sele lubonisa ukuba lufuna ukuqhubeka nokuvota.
Ezi zinto azinakuphinda zenziwe", watsho uGrant Reeher, onguprofesa wezenzululwazi kwezopolitiko kwiSikolo sikaMaxwell saseYunivesithi yaseSyracuse kwiThe Hill kwinqaku elipapashwe ngoMgqibelo.
UReeher uthe uthandabuza ukuba isenzo sokugqibela senkulumbuso uJeff Flake (R-Arizona) sokuphanda kweFBI siya kwanela ukuthulisa abo bavoti.
"Abafazi abayi kulibala oko kwenzekayo izolo - abayi kulibala ngomso yaye abayi kulibala ngoNovemba", watsho njalo uKarin Jean-Pierre, umcebisi ophezulu nesithethi sikazwelonke seqela eliqhubela phambili iMoveOn, ngoLwesihlanu, ngokutsho kwephephandaba laseWashington, D.C.
Ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, ababhikishi babethetha ngelithi "UNovemba uyeza!" njengoko babonisa kwibhodi yeSenate njengoko amaRiphabliki alawula iKomiti yoLungiso lwaMthetho ekhetha ukuqhubela phambili nokumiselwa kukaKavanaugh nangona kukho ubungqina bukaGqr. Christine Blasey Ford, uxele uMic.
UStu Rothenberg, ongengomcebisi wezopolitiko, uxelele le ndawo yeendaba: "Unyamezelo nentshukumisa yentando yesininzi ziya kuphelelwa ngumdla".
"Abantu bathi sele sele iphezulu; oku kuyinyaniso.
Kodwa isenokuba ngaphezulu, ngokukodwa phakathi kwabavoti abasetyhini abahamba phambili kwiidolophu ezisecaleni kunye nabavoti abaselula, abaneminyaka eli-18 ukusa kwengama-29, nangona bengamthandi umongameli, badla ngokungavoti".
Kwanangaphambi kokuba uFord anike ubungqina esidlangalaleni obuchaza izityholo zakhe zokuxhatshazwa ngokwesini kumntu okhethwe kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo, abahlalutyi bathi kusenokulandela impembelelo embi ukuba amaRiphabliki ayaqhubeka nokuqinisekisa.
"Oku kuye kwaba yingxaki kwiqela le-GOP", utshilo uMichael Steele, owayesakuba ngusihlalo weKomiti yeSizwe yamaRiphabliki, ekuqaleni kweveki ephelileyo, ngokwe-NBC News.
"Asikho nje esibhekiselele ekuvoteni kweKomiti okanye ekuvoteni kokugqibela okanye ukuba uKavanaugh ubekwa ebhentshini, kukwakhona ngendlela amaRiphabliki aye aphatha ngayo oku nendlela amphathe ngayo", utshilo uGuy Cecil, umlawuli wePriorities USA, iqela elinceda ukukhetha amaDemocrat, kwijelo leendaba.
Noko ke, kubonakala ngathi amaMerika ahlukene phakathi kokukholelwa ngubani emva kobungqina bukaFord nobukaKavanaugh, yaye aye aphakamisa kancinane icala lale yokugqibela.
Uhlolisiso olutsha olwenziwa nguYouGov lubonisa ukuba iipesenti ezingama-41 zabaphenduli ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi bakholelwa ubungqina bukaFord, ngoxa iipesenti ezingama-35 zithi ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi bayakholelwa uKavanaugh.
Ukongezelela, ama-38% athi acinga ukuba uKavanaugh mhlawumbi okanye ngokuqinisekileyo waxoka ebudeni bobungqina bakhe, ngoxa ama-30% kuphela athi okufanayo ngoFord.
