Umvelisi weWebhu yeHlabathi Ibanzi Uceba Ukuqalisa i-Intanethi Entsha
UTim Berners-Lee, umvelisi weWorld Wide Web, usungula iqonga eliza kuqhudelana neFacebook, iAmazon neGoogle.
Iprojekthi yakutshanje ye-tech legend, i-Inrupt, yinkampani eyakha kwiqonga likaBerners-Lee elivulekileyo elinguSolid.
I-Solid ivumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe apho idatha yabo igcinwa khona kwaye abantu bavunyelwe ukuba bafikelele kuluphi ulwazi.
Kwi-interview ekhethekileyo ne-Fast Company, uBerners-Lee wancwina esithi injongo ephambili ye-Inrupt "kukulawula umhlaba".
Wathi xa ethetha ngokuqalisa.
"Lilixesha lembali".
Le app isebenzisa iteknoloji kaSolid ukuvumela abantu ukuba benze "indawo yokugcina idatha yobuqu kwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Inokuqulatha uluhlu lwabantu abanxibelelana nabo, uluhlu lwezinto ekufuneka zenziwe, ikhalenda, ithala lomculo nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezobuchule.
Kunjengokuba iGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify zonke zifumaneka kwisikhangeli esinye kwaye zonke ngexesha elinye.
Into ekhethekileyo kwivenkile yokugcina idatha yobuqu ye-intanethi kukuba ixhomekeke ngokupheleleyo kumsebenzisi ukuba ngubani onokufikelela kuluphi uhlobo lolwazi.
Le nkampani ithi "ukuxhobisa abantu ngokusebenzisa idatha".
Ingcamango ye-Inrupt, ngokutsho kwe-CEO yenkampani uJohn Bruce, kukuba inkampani izise izixhobo, iinkqubo kunye nezakhono ezifanelekileyo ukunceda ukwenza iSolide ifumaneke kubo bonke.
Inkampani ngoku iquka uBerners-Lee, uBruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elithengwe yi-IBM, abanye abaphuhlisi abasebenza kwiprojekthi, kunye noluntu lwababhalisi abazinikeleyo.
Ukususela kule veki, abaphuhlisi bezobuchwepheshe ehlabathini lonke banokuzenzela iiapps zabo ezingasebenziyo besebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee uthe yena neqela lakhe abaxeleli "i-Facebook neGoogle ukuba ingaba baya kwenza utshintsho olupheleleyo okanye hayi apho zonke iimodeli zabo zoshishino ziphantse ziguquke ngobusuku obunye.
"Asizukucela imvume yabo".
Kwiposti kwiMedium epapashwe ngoMgqibelo, uBerners-Lee wabhala ukuba "umsebenzi we-Inrupt kukubonelela ngombane wezorhwebo kunye nenkqubo yendalo yokunceda ukukhusela ingqibelelo nomgangatho wewebhu entsha eyakhiwe kwiSolid".
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee waguqula i-intanethi xa waseka iWorld Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee uye waba lilizwi elinamandla kwingxoxo yokungathathi cala kwenethiwekhi.
Nangona eqalisa i-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuhlala engumSunguli kunye noMlawuli weWorld Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation kunye ne-Open Data Institute.
UBerners-Lee wongezelela wathi: "Ndiqinisekile ukuba eli xesha liza kubakho".
