Desert Island Discs: UTom Daley wayeziva 'ephantsi' ngokwesini
UTom Daley uthi wakhula eziva engekho mhle kunabanye abantu ngenxa yesondo lakhe - kodwa oko kwamenza waba nempumelelo.
Lo mntwana oneminyaka engama-24 ubudala wathi akazange aqonde de waya esikolweni esiphakamileyo ukuba "abantwini bonke abafana nam".
Ethetha kwiRadio 4 Desert Island Discs yokuqala eboniswa nguLauren Laverne, wathi wathetha ngamalungelo abantu abangamakhwenkwe angamafanasini ukuze anike abanye "ithemba".
Kwakhona wathi ukuba ngumzali kwamenza angabi nomdla wokuphumelela kwiiOlimpiki.
Umqhubi oqhelekileyo wale nkqubo, uKirsty Young, uye wathabatha ikhefu leenyanga ezininzi ngenxa yokugula.
Ebonakala njengendoda elahlekileyo kwinkqubo yokuqala kaLaverne, uDaley wathi wayeziva "engaphantsi" kunabanye abantu abakhulayo kuba "kwakungamkelekanga ngokwasentlalweni ukuthanda amakhwenkwe namantombazana".
Wathi: "Ude kube namhlanje, loo mivakalelo yokuziva ndingento yanto, nokuziva ndihlukile, yeyona nto indinike amandla namandla okuphumelela".
Wathi wayefuna ukubonisa ukuba "nguthile", ukuze angalahlekisi wonke umntu xa ekugqibeleni efumanisa ngesondo sakhe.
Umdlali weembasa zeOlimpiki ezibini zobhedu uye waba ngumkhuthazi we-LGBT ophakamileyo kwaye wasebenzisa ukubonakala kwakhe kwiMidlalo ye-Commonwealth kulo nyaka eOstreliya ukuze abongoze amazwe amaninzi ukuba aphelise ubufanasini.
Wathi wathetha kuba wayeziva enethamsanqa ngokuba nokuphila ngokucacileyo ngaphandle kweemiphumo yaye wayefuna ukunika abanye "ithemba".
Lo mdlali weqonga wehlabathi kathathu wathi ukuthandana nomntu - umenzi wefilimu waseMerika uDustin Lance Black, awadibana naye ngowama-2013 - "kwandichukumisa".
UDaley watshata nomntu owaphumelela iOscar, oneminyaka engama-20 kunaye, kunyaka ophelileyo kodwa wathi umehluko wobudala awuzange ube yingxaki.
"Xa uselula kangaka, uye kwiiOlimpiki zokuqala eneminyaka eli-14 yaye uyise wabulawa ngumhlaza kwiminyaka emithathu kamva", wathi kwakunzima ukufumana umntu oneminyaka elifanayo naye owayeye wajamelana neengxaki ezifanayo.
Esi sibini saba ngabazali ngoJuni, sonyana ogama linguRobert Ray Black-Daley, yaye uDaley wathi "umbono wakhe uphela" utshintshile.
Wathi: "Ukuba ubundibuze kunyaka ophelileyo, bekuza kuba ngathi 'Ndifuna ukufumana imbasa yegolide.'
"Kukho izinto ezinkulu kuneembasa zegolide zeOlimpiki.
Igolide yam yeOlimpiki nguRobbie".
Unyana wakhe unalo igama elifanayo noyise uRobert, owafayo ngowama-2011 eneminyaka engama-40 emva kokufumanisa ukuba unesifo somhlaza wengqondo.
UDaley wathi utata wakhe akazange avume ukuba uza kufa yaye enye yezinto zokugqibela awayezibuze ukuba ngaba banamatikiti abo eLondon 2012 - njengoko wayefuna ukuba kumqolo wokuqala.
Wathi: "Andinakumxelela ukuba 'awusayi kuba sedolophu ukuba ube kumqolo wokuqala, utata.'"
Wathi: "Ndandimthatha ngesandla xa wayeka ukuphefumla yaye kwakuphela xa wayeka ukuphefumla waza wafa xa ndaqonda ukuba akanako ukoyiswa".
Kunyaka olandelayo uDaley wancintisana kwiiOlimpiki zika-2012 waza waphumelela ithsaba.
Wathi: "Ndandiqonda ukuba le yinto ebendiyifuna ubomi bam bonke - ukubhukuqa phambi kwesihlwele sasekhaya kwiMidlalo yeOlimpiki, kwakungekho mvakalelo ibhetele", watsho.
Kwakhona yaphefumlela ukhetho lwakhe lokuqala lwengoma - Proud nguHeather Small - eyayimkhuthazile ekwakheni iOlimpiki kwaye isamenza azive enqena.
