UMickelson ongenamzimba wahlala ebhentshini kwiRyder Cup ngoMgqibelo
UmMerika uPhil Mickelson uza kubeka irekhodi ngeCawa xa edlala umdlalo wakhe wama-47 weRyder Cup, kodwa kuya kufuneka aguqule ifomu yakhe ukuze aphephe ukuba ngumnyhadala ongathandekiyo.
UMickelson, owayedlala kumnyhadala wamabini ngonyaka okwesihlandlo sesibini, wabekwa ebhentshini nguJim Furyk ukuze adlale imidlalo yomgqibelo.
Kunokuba abe phakathi kwezinto ezenzekayo, njengoko ebesoloko esenza eUnited States, lo mdlali uphumelele izihlandlo ezihlanu wachitha usuku lwakhe phakathi kokuba ngumqhubi weentshukumisa nokusebenza kumdlalo wakhe kwintsimi enethemba lokulungisa oko kumhluphayo.
Akayena oyena mqhubi ubalaseleyo, kwanasekuqaliseni komsebenzi wakhe, lo mdlali oneminyaka engama-48 ubudala akanguye ofanelekileyo kwikhadi elinzima leLe Golf National, apho umqhubi omde onzima ehlala esohlwaya iintambo ezingachanekanga.
Yaye ukuba ikhosi ngokwayo ayisiyonto inzima ngokwaneleyo, uMickelson, kumdlalo wesithoba ngeCawa, uza kujamelana neBritish Open ingqwelwana echanekileyo uFrancesco Molinari, oye wahlangana nomtsha-ntliziyo uTommy Fleetwood ukuze aphumelele yonke imidlalo yakhe emine kule veki.
Ukuba amaMerika, anamanqaku amane asezantsi ekuqaliseni imidlalo ye-12 ye-singles, ayaqala kakuhle, umdlalo kaMickelson unokuba yinto ebalulekileyo.
UFuryk wabonisa ukuba uyamthemba, kungekhona ukuba wayenokuthetha okungakumbi.
UFuryk uthi: "Wayiqonda ngokupheleleyo indima yakhe namhlanje, wandibetha ngasemva waza wandibamba ngesandla wathi uza kuba ekulungele ngomso".
"Uzithemba kakhulu.
Ungumdlali weHall of Fame yaye uye wongeza izinto ezininzi kula maqela kwixesha elidlulileyo, nakule veki.
Mhlawumbi ndandingazange ndimcinge edlala imidlalo emibini.
Ndandikucinga oku, kodwa kwakusenzeka ngaloo ndlela, yaye sasicinga ukuba simele sihambe ngaloo ndlela.
Ufuna ukuba phandle, njengabo bonke abanye".
UMickelson uza kudlula irekhodi likaNick Faldo kwimidlalo emininzi yeRyder Cup edlalwe ngeCawa.
Oku kusenokubonisa ukuphela komsebenzi wakhe weRyder Cup ongazange ufanelane nokuphuma kwerekhodi yakhe.
UMickelson unama-18 okuphumelela, ama-20 okulahlekelwa kunye nama-7 okuhlula, nangona uFuryk wathi ubukho bakhe buzise izinto ezingabonakaliyo kwiqela.
Wachaza: "Uyahlekisa, uyacaphukisa, unobulumko, uthanda ukuhlekisa ngabantu, yaye ungumntu omhle ukuba naye ekamelweni lamaqela".
"Ndicinga ukuba abadlali abaselula babenandipha ukuzama ukumbulala, kule veki, nto leyo eyayimnandi ukuyibona.
