Ngoko imbali iya kubonisa kum nakwabo bonke abasele bekulo qela ukuba oku akukapheli.
Uya kuhlutha ngomso.
Hamba uye kwenza izinto ezilungileyo.
Oku akupheli de ube sele ufumene amanqaku ebhodini.
Sinenjongo, yaye oko kukuthi, ukuzama ukuphumelela le ndebe, yaye apho kugxininiswa khona.
Bendisoloko ndisithi, ndijonge abadlali abali-12 abakwicala lethu, kodwa siyazi kakuhle into eyenzeka kwelinye icala - abadlali abakhulu ehlabathini".
