"Ndandihamba neqela labafana kolu ngcelele kuba ndicinga ukuba lugubungela yonke indlela", utshilo uBjorn malunga nokukhethwa kwakhe kwee-singles.
Inqanawa entsha yemfazwe yaseJamani yaphinda yahlulwa
I-Fregate entsha ye-Navy yaseJamani yayimele ukuba yathunyelwa ngo-2014 ukubuyisela iinqanawa zemfazwe zexesha leMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa ayiyi kuba khona ubuncinane kunyaka olandelayo ngenxa yeenkqubo ezingachanekanga kunye neendleko ze-snowballing, kwaxelwa ngamajelo asekuhlaleni.
Ukufakwa kwe "Rheinland-Pfalz", inqanawa ephambili yeebhodi ezintsha zeBaden-Wuerttemberg, ngoku kuye kwacothwa ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-2019, ngokutsho kwephephandaba iDie Zeit ecaphula isithethi somkhosi.
Inqanawa ibifanele ukuba yajoyina iMarine ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki eziphazamisayo emva kokuhanjiswa zabetha isahlulo seprojekthi enqwenelekayo.
Iinqanawa ezine zeklasi yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg eziyalelwe yiMarine ngowama-2007 ziya kuza njengendawo yeefrigate ezikhulayo zeklasi yaseBremen.
Kuqondwa ukuba ziya kuba nompu onamandla, uthotho lweentsholongwane ezichasene nomoya nezitshabalalisi-nqanawa kunye neetekhnoloji ezithile ezifihlakeleyo, ezinje nge-radar encitshisiweyo, i-infrared kunye ne-acoustic signatures.
Ezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo ziquka ixesha elide lokugcina - kufuneka kube lula ukuthumela ii-frigates ezintsha ukuya kwiminyaka emibini kude nezibuko lasekhaya.
Noko ke, ukulibaziseka okuqhubekayo kuthetha ukuba iinqanawa zemfazwe eziphambili - ekuthiwa ziza kuvumela iJamani ukuba ikwazi ukuvelisa amandla phesheya - ziya kuba zingasasebenzi xa ziqalisa ukusebenza, utsho uDie Zeit.
I-F125 eyaba yintlekele yafika kwiingqungquthela kunyaka ophelileyo, xa i-Navy yaseJamani yawala ngokusemthethweni ukuyisebenzisa inqanawa yaza yabuyisela kwi-Blohm & Voss shipyard eHamburg.
Eli yayilixesha lokuqala ukuba iMarine ibuyisele inqanawa kumakhi wenqanawa emva kokuziswa.
Kwakungaziwa kangako ngezizathu zokubuyela, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani athetha "ngeempazamo zesoftware nezixhobo" ezazenza le nqanawa ingasebenzi xa isetyenziswa kwimisebenzi yemfazwe.
Iintsilelo zesoftware zazibaluleke ngokukhethekileyo kuba iinqanawa zeklasi yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg ziya kusetyenziswa ngabanini-zinqanawa abamalunga nama-120 - isiqingatha nje somsebenzi weenqanawa ezindala zeklasi yaseBremen.
Kwakhona, kwavela ukuba inqanawa inobunzima obukhulu obunciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye ikhawuleze amandla oMkhosi wezasolwandle okongeza ukuphuculwa kwexesha elizayo.
I-"Rheinland-Pfalz" enobunzima beetoni ezingama - 7,000 ikholelwa ukuba inzima kabini kunenqanawa eklasi efanayo eyayisetyenziswa ngamaJamani kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ngaphandle kwezinto ezinesiphene, ixabiso leprojekthi yonke - kuquka uqeqesho lwabasebenzi - nalo liza kuba yingxaki.
Kuxelwa ukuba iye yafikelela kwi-3,1 yezigidigidi ze-euro (i-3,6 yezigidigidi zeedola) - ukusuka kwi-2,2 yezigidigidi zokuqala.
Iingxaki zokubamba iinqanawa ezintsha ziba zibaluleke ngokukhethekileyo ngenxa yezilumkiso zakutshanje zokuba amandla omkhosi waselwandle waseJamani aya anciphisa.
Ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, intloko yekomiti yokhuselo yeparlamente yaseJamani, wavuma ukuba enyanisweni iMarine "iphelelwa ziinqanawa ezinokuthuthwa".
Lo mqeshwa uthe le ngxaki iye yavela ngexesha, kuba iinqanawa ezindala zazisuswa kodwa azange zibonelelwe ngeenqanawa eziza kuzitshintsha.
Wadanisa ukuba akukho nanye kwiifrigati zeklasi yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg ekwazileyo ukujoyina iMarine.
I-National Trust iyamphulaphula ngenyameko ubomi obungafihliyo beebhatshi
Uphando olutsha olwenziwa kwilali yaseScotland Highlands lufuna ukubonisa indlela iimbethe ezisebenzisa ngayo umhlaba xa zifuna ukutya.
Kukho ithemba lokuba ezi zinto zifunyenweyo ziya kukhanyisa indlela eziphatha ngayo izilwanyana ezinambuzane eziphaphazelayo kwaye zikhokele imisebenzi yokulondoloza ikamva.
Uphando olwenziwa zizazinzulu kwiNational Trust for Scotland luya kulandela i-pipristrelles eqhelekileyo ne-soprano kwakunye ne-brown long-eared bats kunye ne-Daubenton bats kwi-Inverewe Gardens eWester Ross.
Kuya kufakwa iirekhodi ezikhethekileyo kwiindawo eziphambili ezijikeleze ipropathi ukuze zilandelwe imisebenzi yeebhatyi ebudeni bexesha lonyaka.
Abasebenzi be-NHS kunye namavolontiya baya kwenza uphando olwenziwayo ngeselula besebenzisa iidetekitors ezikhutshwayo.
Uhlalutyo lwengoma lwengcali kuzo zonke iirekhodi luya kuqinisekisa ukuba zibiza kangakanani iintethe yaye zeziphi iintlobo ezenza ntoni.
Emva koko kuya kwenziwa imephu yendawo yokuhlala kunye nengxelo ukuze kuveliswe umfanekiso onzulu wesikali sendalo ngendlela abaziphatha ngayo.
URob Dewar, umcebisi wokulondolozwa kwendalo kwi-NTS, unethemba lokuba iziphumo ziya kutyhila ukuba zeziphi iindawo zokuhlala ezibaluleke kakhulu kwiintsomi nendlela ezisetyenziswa ngayo kolu hlobo ngalunye.
Olu lwazi luza kunceda ekuchongeni iinzuzo zomsebenzi wokulawula indawo yokuhlala njengokudala amadlelo nendlela efanelekileyo yokugcina amahlathi kwiingcongconi nezinye iintlobo ezinxulumene noko.
Ubuninzi beebhabhathane eScotland naseUnited Kingdom buye bonyuka kakhulu kule nkulungwane idluleyo.
Zisengozini ngenxa yokwakha nokwakha okuchaphazela izindlu zazo nokulahleka kwendalo.
Iindawo zokwakha umoya kunye nokukhanya nazo zinokuba yingozi, njengoko zinokuba njalo amaphepha okuhamba kunye nezinye iindlela zokulungisa izinto zokwakha ngemichiza, kwanokuhlaselwa ziikati ezifuywayo.
Iintsomi aziboni.
Noko ke, ngenxa yemikhwa yabo yokuzingela yasebusuku iindlebe zabo ziluncedo ngakumbi kunamehlo abo xa kufikwa ekubambeni amaxhoba.
Basebenzisa indlela ebalaseleyo yokufumanisa ukuba kukho izinto ezingahambi kakuhle okanye izinto eziphazamisa indlela abahamba ngayo.
I-NTS, enoxanduva lokunyamekela izakhiwo ezingaphezu kwama-270 zembali, iigadi ezingama-38 ezibalulekileyo kunye nama-76,000 eehektare zomhlaba kulo lonke ilizwe, ithatha iintethe nzulu.
Inamagcisa alishumi aqeqeshiweyo, aqhuba rhoqo uphando, ukuhlolwa kweenkuku yaye ngamanye amaxesha neenkcukacha zokusindisa.
Lo mbutho uye waseka indawo yokuqala yaseSkotlani yokugcina iintethe kwipropati yaseThreave eDumfries naseGalloway, apho kuhlala khona iintlobo ezisibhozo kwezilishumi zeentethe zaseSkotlani.
Umphathi wepropati uDavid Thompson uthi le ndawo yeyona ndawo ifanelekileyo kubo.
"Nantsi e Threave sinendawo enkulu yeengcongconi", watsho.
"Sinezakhiwo ezindala, imithi emininzi yamaxesha amandulo kunye nendawo yokuhlala elungileyo.
Kodwa zininzi izinto ezingaziwa ngeengcungcu, ngoko umsebenzi esiwenzayo apha nakwezinye iindawo uya kusinceda siqonde ngakumbi oko zifuna ukukwenza ukuze zikhule".
UGqogqa ukubaluleka kokujonga ukuba kukho iimbethe ngaphambi kokwenza ulondolozo kwipropathi njengoko kunokwenzeka ukuba ukutshabalalisa okungaqondanga indawo enye yokubeleka kunokubulala amabhinqa kunye nabantwana abangama-400, mhlawumbi kutshabalalise bonke abantu basekuhlaleni.
Iintsomi zikhuselwe kwaye akukho mthethweni ukubulala, ukuzikhathaza okanye ukuphazamisa okanye ukutshabalalisa amaqabunga azo.
UElisabeth Ferrell, igosa laseSkotlani leBat Conservation Trust, uye wakhuthaza uluntu ukuba luzinikele ekuncedeni.
Wathi: "Sisafanele sifunde okuninzi ngeentethe zethu yaye kwiintlobo zethu ezininzi asiyazi indlela ezihamba ngayo".
URonaldo uyazigatya izityholo zokudlwengula njengoko amagqwetha eza kumangalela imagazini yaseJamani
UChristiano Ronaldo ubeke isimangalo sokudlwengulwa kwakhe ngokuthi "ziindaba ezingezizo", esithi abantu "bafuna ukuzithengisa" ngokusebenzisa igama lakhe.
Amagqwetha akhe aza kumangalela umboneleli weendaba waseJamani uDer Spiegel, owapapasha izityholo.
Umdlali wePortugal noJuventus utyholwa ngokudlwengula ibhinqa laseMerika, eligama linguKathryn Mayorga, kwigumbi laseLas Vegas kwihotele ngo-2009.
Kuthiwa wahlawula i-375.000 yeedola ukuze angathi nto, njengoko iDer Spiegel ibhale ngoLwesihlanu.
Ethetha kwividiyo ye-Instagram Live kubalandeli bakhe abazizigidi ezili-142 kwiiyure emva kokuba ezi zityholo zibikiwe, uRonaldo, oneminyaka engama-33 ubudala, wazigxeka ezi ngxelo ngokuthi "ziindaba ezingezizo".
"Hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi.
Oko bakutshoyo namhlanje, iindaba ezingezizo", utsho lo uphumelele izihlandlo ezihlanu kwiBallon d'Or ekhamera.
"Bafuna ukuzithengisa besebenzisa igama lam.
Kuyinto eqhelekileyo.
Bafuna ukuba nodumo ukuze bathi igama lam, kodwa kuyinxalenye yomsebenzi.
Ndingumntu onoyolo yaye ndilungile", wongezelela lo mdlali, emomotheka.
