UM Mayorga ukwathetha ukuba waya emapoliseni waza wathatha iifoto zokwenzakala kwakhe esibhedlele, kodwa kamva wavuma ukuxoxwa kwetyala ngaphandle kwenkundla kuba wayeziva "esoyika impindezelo" kwaye wayekhathazekile "ngokuhlaziswa esidlangalaleni".
