I-Brexit: UK 'iya kuzisola ngonaphakade' ngokulahlekelwa ngabenzi beemoto
UK "iya kulizisola ngonaphakade" ukuba iya kuphulukana nesikhundla sayo njengenkokeli yehlabathi kwimveliso yeemoto emva kweBrexit, utshilo uNobhala wezoShishino uGreg Clark.
Wongezelela ukuba "kuxhalabisa" ukuba iToyota UK yaxelela iBBC ukuba ukuba iBritani iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano iya kuyeka okwethutyana imveliso kumzi mveliso wayo eBurnaston, kufuphi neDerby.
UMnu Clark wathi: "Sifuna isivumelwano".
Umvelisi weemoto waseJapan wathi impembelelo yokunqunyanyiswa kwemida kwimeko yeBrexit engenazo izivumelwano inokubiza imisebenzi.
Umzi mveliso waseBurnaston - owenza iAuris neAvensis zikaToyota - wavelisa iimoto ezimalunga ne-150,000 kunyaka ophelileyo apho i-90% yayo yathunyelwa kwamanye amazwe aseYurophu.
"Ndicinga ukuba ukuba iBritani iya kuphuma kwi-EU ekupheleni kukaMatshi siza kubona imveliso iyeka kumzi-mveliso wethu", utshilo uMarvin Cooke, umlawuli ophetheyo weToyota eBurnaston.
Abanye abavelisi bezithuthi base-UK baye baveza inkxalabo malunga nokuphuma kwi-EU ngaphandle kokuvumelana ngendlela urhwebo olungaphaya kwemida oluya kusebenza ngayo, kuquka uHonda, iBMW kunye neJaguar Land Rover.
Ngokomzekelo, iBMW ithi iza kuvala umzi-mveliso wayo omncinane eOxford kangangeenyanga emva kweBrexit.
Eyona nto ixhalabisayo kukuba, abavelisi beemoto bathi banokubeka engozini imixokelelwane yokuthengisa xa kukho iBrexit ngaphandle kwesivumelwano.
Umgca wemveliso kaToyota uqhutywa "ngokufanelekileyo", kunye neenxalenye ezifika rhoqo emva kwemizuzu engama-37 zivela kubathengisi base-UK nase-EU kwiimoto ezenziwe ngokwezifiso.
Ukuba i-UK iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngomhla wama-29 Matshi, kunokubakho ukuphazamiseka kumda okuya kuthi kushishino kunokubangela ukulibaziseka kunye nokunqongophala kwezinto.
Le nkampani yathi, ayinakwenzeka ukuba iToyota igcine izinto ezingaphezulu kosuku olunye kumzi-mveliso wayo waseDerbyshire, ngoko imveliso iya kumiswa.
UMnu Clark wathi isicwangciso sikaTheresa May seChequers sobudlelwane bexesha elizayo ne-EU "sichaneke ngokuchanekileyo ukuze kuphephe ukuhlolwa komda".
"Kufuneka senze isivumelwano. Sifuna ukuba nesivumelwano esihle kakhulu esiya kuvumela ukuba, njengoko ndithetha, singavuyi nje impumelelo yangoku kodwa ukuba sifumane eli thuba", utshilo kwinkqubo ye-BBC Radio 4's Today.
"Ubungqina obungaveli kwiToyota kuphela kodwa nakwezinye iinkampani ezenzileyo bubonisa ukuba kufuneka siqhubeke nokwenza izinto eziphumelelayo".
I-Toyota ayizange ikwazi ukuchaza ukuba imveliso iza kuvalwa ixesha elingakanani, kodwa kwixesha elide, yalumkisa ukuba iindleko ezongeziweyo ziya kunciphisa ukhuphiswano lwesityalo kwaye ekugqibeleni zilahlekelwe yimisebenzi.
UPeter Tsouvallaris, osebe eBurnaston iminyaka engama-24 yaye engumhlanganisi wequmrhu le-Unite kule mboni, wathi amalungu akhe aya exhalabile: "Ngokwamava am, xa ezi zikhundla ziyekile, aziphindi zibuyele.
Isithethi sikarhulumente sathi: "Sibeke isicwangciso esicacileyo nesithembekileyo sobuhlobo bethu bexesha elizayo ne-EU".
Indlu Emhlophe ithi intlanganiso kaTrump noRosenstein isenokulibaziseka kwakhona
Intlanganiso kaDonald Trump kunye nomgcini-sicelo uRod Rosenstein "inokubuyiselwa emva kwiveki enye" njengoko umlo malunga nomntu okhethwe kwiNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh uqhubeka, i-White House ithe ngeCawa.
URosenstein ulawula umsebenzi womcebisi okhethekileyo uRobert Mueller, ophanda ngokungenelela kweRashiya kunyulo, unxibelelwano phakathi kwabancedisi bakaTrump neRashiya kunye nokuthintelwa kokusesikweni ngumongameli.
Enoba uTrump uza kumgxotha na uSekela-Mtshutshisi Jikelele, aze ngaloo ndlela abeke esichengeni ukuzimela kukaMuler, uye wabangela ukuba iWashington ihlabe indlebe kangangeenyanga.
Ekuqaleni kwale nyanga, iNew York Times yathi uRosenstein wayexubusha ngokusetyenziswa kweengcingo ukuze aqokelele iingxoxo noTrump kunye nokwenzeka kokurhoxisa umongameli nge-25th Amendment.
URosenstein waliphika elo xwebhu.
Kodwa ngoMvulo ophelileyo waya kwiNdlu yoMhlophe, phakathi kweengxelo zokuba wayeza kushiya.
Kunoko, kwabhengezwa intlanganiso noTrump, owayesakuba kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo eNew York, ngoLwesine.
UTrump wathi "ngokwangoku angathanda" ukulahla uRosenstein kodwa ke intlanganiso yalibaziseka ukuze kuphephe ukungqubana neKomiti yezoBulungisa yeSenate apho uKavanaugh kunye nomnye wabasetyhini abamangalele ngokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesondo, uGqr. Christine Blasey Ford, bobabini banikela ubungqina.
NgoLwesihlanu, uTrump wayalela ukuba iFBI iphonononge amabango kaKavanaugh kangangeveki enye, nto leyo eyeka ukuvota ngokupheleleyo kwiSenate.
Unobhala kaTrump, uSarah Sanders, wabonakala kwiFox News ngeCawa.
Xa ebuzwa ngentlanganiso yaseRosenstein, wathi: "Umhla wokuza kuhlangana akuzange umiselwe, kusenokwenzeka ukuba bekusekuqaleni kwale veki, ndibona ukuba oko kuya kuqhubeka emva kweveki enye xa kuthathelwa ingqalelo ezinye izinto ezenzekayo kwinkundla ephakamileyo.
Kodwa siza kubona yaye ndithanda ukuqhubeka ndihlaziya iindaba".
Abanye abaxhasi beendaba baya kulahla loo mbono: USanders akazange abambe intetho yeendaba kwiNdlu yoMhlophe ukususela ngoSeptemba 10.
Umamkeli wevidiyo uChris Wallace wabuza isizathu.
USanders wathi ukungabikho kweengxelo akubangelwa kukungafuni kwabo babhali beTV "ababalaseleyo", nangona wathi: "Andiyi kuxabana nento yokuba bebukhulu".
Emva koko wathi kuya kwandiswa unxibelelwano oluthe ngqo phakathi kukaTrump kunye neendaba.
Wathi: "UMongameli wenza iintlanganiso ezininzi ze-Q&A kunaye nawuphi na umongameli ngaphambi kwakhe", wongezelela esithi ngaphandle kokubhekisela kubungqina: "Sikhe sajonga ezo manani".
USanders wathi, iza kubakho iintetho, kodwa "ukuba abezindaba banethuba lokubuza umongameli waseUnited States imibuzo ngokuthe ngqo, oko kungcono kakhulu kunokuthetha nam.
Sizama ukwenza oko rhoqo kwaye nisibonile sisenza oko rhoqo kwiiveki ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo kwaye oko kuya kuthatha indawo yeengxoxo zonxibelelwano xa unokuthetha nomongameli waseUnited States".
UTrump uhlala ephendula imibuzo xa ephuma kwiNdlu yaseMhlophe okanye ethatha inxaxheba kwiiseshoni ezivulekileyo okanye kwiinkomfa zonxibelelwano nabanye abantu ababekho.
Iinkomfa zonxibelelwano zabanye abantu zinqabile.
KwiNew York kule veki umongameli mhlawumbi wabonisa isizathu, esenza ukubonakala okuzenzekelayo yaye ngamanye amaxesha okuyinqaba phambi kweentatheli ezihlanganisene.
UNobhala wezeMpilo ubhalela abasebenzi base-EU kwi-NHS yaseScotland ngenxa yokoyika iBrexit
UMphathiswa wezempilo ubhalele abasebenzi be-EU abasebenza kwi-NHS yaseScotland ukuvakalisa umbulelo welizwe kunye nomnqweno wokuba bahlale emva kweBrexit.
UJeane Freeman MSP wathumela ileta eneenyanga ezingaphantsi kwezithoba ngaphambi kokuba i-UK ishiye i-EU.
Urhulumente waseScotland sele uzibophelele ekuhlaleni iindleko zezicelo zesimo sokuhlala esilungisiweyo kubemi be-EU abasebenza kwiinkonzo zikawonkewonke ezihanjiswe.
Kwileta yakhe, uNksz Freeman wabhala: "Ehlotyeni, iingxoxo phakathi kwe-UK ne-EU zokurhoxa ziye zaqhubeka, zisiya kwizigqibo ezilindelekileyo kule ntlango.
Kodwa urhulumente wase-UK uye wanciphisa amalungiselelo akhe okufumana imeko yokungabikho kwesivumelwano.
Ndiyazi ukuba eli lixesha elixhalabisayo kuni nonke.
Ngoko ke ndifuna ukuphinda ndiphinde ndivakalise indlela endiyixabisa ngayo igalelo lamalungu onke abasebenzi, kungakhathaliseki ukuba ngabaluphi uhlanga.
Abahlobo abavela kulo lonke elase-EU nangaphaya, bazisa amava namava axabisekileyo aqhuba umsebenzi wenkonzo yezempilo, aze alungelelanise, yaye aluncedo kwizigulana nakwimimandla esiyincedayo.
IScotland likhaya lakho yaye sifuna kakhulu ukuba uhlale apha".
