Eli nyathelo liya kubangela ukuba uCorbyn angakwazi ukuphumelela kumzamo wakhe wokutsala abavoti abaselula
Ukunyuka komrhumo wezitampu kuya kuhlawuliswa kwabo bangabhatali rhafu e-UK
I-Treasury ilindele ukuba ifumane ukuya kutsho kwi-120 yezigidi ze-Â£ ngonyaka- ukunceda abangenamakhaya
Abathengi bamanye amazwe baya kuhlawuliswa irhafu ephezulu xa bethenga ipropathi e-UK - kunye nemali eyongezelelweyo esetyenziselwa ukunceda abangenamakhaya, uTheresa May uza kuvakalisa namhlanje.
Esi sigqibo siza kuthathwa njengento yokuzama ukuthintela impumelelo yomzamo kaJeremy Corbyn wokutsala abavoti abaselula abanesifungo sokubonelela ngezindlu ezifikelelekayo kunye nokujolisa kubantu abafumana imali ephezulu.
Ukunyuka kwamatyala esitifiketi kuya kuhlawuliswa kubantu ngabanye nakwimibutho engakhokheli rhafu e-UK, kunye nemali eyongezelelweyo ekhuthaza umzamo karhulumente wokulwa nokulala kanzima.
I-surcharge - eyongezelelweyo kwinto esele isetyenziswe njengentlawulo yesitampu, kuquka amanqanaba aphezulu aqale asetyenziswa kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo kumakhaya ase-Buy-to-Lets - inokuba ngama-3%.
I-Treasury ilindele ukuba eli nyathelo liphakamise ukuya kuthi ga kwi-120 yezigidi ze-Â£ ngonyaka.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba iipesenti ezili-13 zezindlu ezakhiwe eLondon zithengwa ngabantu abangengabo abemi base-UK, nto leyo eyenza amaxabiso anyuke kwaye yenza kube nzima ukuba abathengi bokuqala bangene kwizindlu.
Imimandla emininzi esisityebi kweli lizwe - ingakumbi eyintloko - iye yaba "ziidolophu eziziziphoso" ngenxa yenani elikhulu labathengi bamanye amazwe abachitha ixesha labo elininzi ngaphandle kweli lizwe.
Le nkqubo intsha iza emva nje kweeveki ezimbalwa uBoris Johnson efuna ukuncitshiswa komrhumo wezitampu ukunceda ulutsha oluninzi ukuba lube nekhaya lokuqala.
Watyhola iinkampani ezinkulu zokwakha ngokugcina amaxabiso epropati ephezulu ngokuthabatha umhlaba kodwa ungawusebenzisi, waza wabongoza uNkosikazi May ukuba ayeke ukuhlawula izindlu ezifikelelekayo ukuze alungise "ihlazo lezindlu" laseBritani.
UMnu Corbyn ubhengeze uthotho olumangalisayo lweziphakamiso zokuhlaliswa kwezindlu, kuquka ukulawulwa kwemizi kunye nokupheliswa kokuqhutywa kwabantu "ngaphandle kwesizathu".
Kwakhona ufuna ukunika iibhunga igunya elingakumbi lokwakha amakhaya amatsha.
UMnu. May wathi: "Ngo nyaka ophelileyo ndathi ndiza kunikela ubuntloko bam ekubuyiseleni iphupha laseBritani - lokuba ubomi bufanele bube bhetele kwisizukulwana ngasinye esitsha.
Oko kuthetha ukulungisa imarike yethu yezindlu.
IBritani iya kuhlala ivulelekile kubantu abafuna ukuhlala, ukusebenza nokwakha ubomi apha.
Noko ke, akunakwenzeka ukuba kube lula kubantu abangabemi e-UK, kwakunye neenkampani zasemzini, ukuthenga amakhaya njengabantu baseBritani abasebenza nzima.
Kubantu abaninzi iphupha lokuba ngumnini-mzi lide kakhulu, yaye ukuhlazeka kokulala nzima kuhlala kuyinyani".
