UHolly Snyder, osekela-mongameli we-Nationwide kwishishini le-inshorensi yobomi uthi: "Abantu bafuna ilungu lentsapho libanakekele, kodwa abazithathi amanyathelo okuqhuba incoko".
Nantsi indlela yokuqalisa.
Thetha neqabane lakho nabantwana: Awunakukwazi ukunceda intsapho yakho ukuba inyamekele abantwana ukuba awuzange ubazise kwangaphambili.
Sebenzisana nomcebisi wakho nosapho lwakho ukuze nixoxe ngendawo nendlela yokunyamekela, kuba ezi zigqibo zinokuba nempembelelo enkulu ekumiseleni iindleko.
Yiza nomcebisi wakho wezemali: Umcebisi wakho unokunceda ufumane indlela yokuhlawula ezo ndleko.
Ukhetho lwakho lwemali yokunyamekela ixesha elide lunokuquka umgaqo-nkqubo weshishini lokunyamekela ixesha elide, umgaqo-nkqubo weshishini lokunyamekela ubomi obunexabiso eliphantsi ukuze uhlawulele ezi ndleko okanye ukuzinceda ngokwakho ngobutyebi bakho - logama nje unemali.
Hambisa amaxwebhu akho asemthethweni uze uqalise ukulwa nemibambano esemthethweni.
Fumana ummeli wezempilo ukuze umisele umntu omthembayo oza kulawula unyango lwakho uze uqinisekise ukuba iingcali ziyazithobela izicelo zakho ukuba awukwazi ukunxibelelana.
Kwakhona, cinga ngegunya lommeli lezemali.
Uyakhetha umntu omthembayo oza kukwenzela izigqibo zemali uze uqinisekise ukuba iirhafu zakho ziyahlawulwa ukuba awunakukwazi ukuzenza izinto.
Ungaze ulibale iinkcukacha ezincinane: Masithi umzali wakho osekhulile unengxaki engxamisekileyo yaye usendleleni eya esibhedlele.
Ngaba ungakwazi ukuphendula imibuzo ephathelele amayeza okanye izinto ezinganyangekiyo?
Bhala ezi nkcukacha phantsi ukuze ulungele.
UMartin wabuza: "Asikokwemali kuphela okuphazamisayo, kodwa ngoobani oogqirha?"
"Ziziphi iziyobisi?
Ngubani oza kukhathalela le nja?
Yenza loo nto".
Indoda yadutyulwa izihlandlo ezininzi ngompu womoya eIlfracombe
Indoda iye yadutyulwa izihlandlo eziliqela ngompu womoya njengoko yayihamba ibuyela ekhaya emva kokuphuma ebusuku.
Ixhoba, elineminyaka engama-40 ubudala, lalisendaweni yaseOxford Grove eIlfracombe, eDevon, xa ladubula esifubeni, esiswini nasesandleni.
Amagosa achaza ukuba ukudubula, okwenzeka malunga ne-2:30 BST, "kwakuyinto eyenzekayo".
Ixhoba alizange libone umhlaseli walo.
Ukulimala kwakhe akubangel' umngcipheko ebomini yaye amapolisa aye afuna amangqina.
Iinyikima neetsunami eIndonesia
Amagosa athi, abantu abamalunga nabayi-384 babulawa yinyikima ne-tsunami enkulu eyahlasela isixeko sasePalu eIndonesia ngoLwesihlanu, yaye kulindeleke ukuba inani labantu abafileyo lenyuke.
Ekubeni unxibelelwano lungasebenzi, amagosa okunceda akakwazanga ukufumana naluphi na ulwazi kwiDonggala regency, ummandla osemantla ePalu osondele kwincopho yenyikima enkulu enobukhulu obungu-7.5.
EPalu, abantu abangaphezu kwe-16,000 baphunyezwa emva kwentlekele.
Nazi ezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo ngePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseSulawesi:
IPalu likomkhulu lephondo laseCentral Sulawesi, elise ekupheleni kwebhayithi emxinwa kunxweme olusentshona kwesi siqithi saseSulawesi, elinabemi abaqikelelwa kwi-379,800 ngo-2017.
Esi sixeko sasibhiyozela iminyaka engama-40 siphile xa kwabakho inyikima netsunami.
I-Donggala sisixeko esihlala ngaphezu kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 kunxweme olusemntla-ntshona wesiqithi saseSulawesi.
I-regency, indawo yolawulo ngaphantsi kwephondo, yayinabantu abaqikelelweyo abangama-299,200 ngo-2017.
Ukuloba nokulima zizinto eziphambili kuqoqosho lwephondo laseCentral Sulawesi, ingakumbi kummandla wolwandle wase Donggala.
Imigodi ye nickel nayo ibalulekile kweli phondo, kodwa ikakhulu igxininiswe eMorowali, kunxweme olungaphaya kweSulawesi.
Ngokutsho kweArhente yaseIndonesia Yokunciphisa Iintlekele, iPalu neDonggala ziye zathintelwa ziitsunami izihlandlo eziliqela kule minyaka iyi-100 idluleyo.
Ngowe-1938, i-tsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 yaza yatshatyalalisa izindlu ezingamakhulu eDonggala.
Ngowe-1996 neTsunami yahlasela intshona yeDonggala, yabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ihlala kwiRing of Fire yasePasifiki yaye ihlala ixhatshazwa ziinyikima.
Nazi ezinye zeenyikima ezinkulu neetsunami kule minyaka idlulileyo:
Ngowama-2004: Inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona yephondo laseAceh eIndonesia kumantla eSumatra ngoDisemba 26 yabangela ukuba kubekho i-tsunami eyahlasela amazwe ali-14, yabulala abantu abangama-226 000 kunxweme loLwandlekazi lwaseIndiya, ngaphezu kwesiqingatha sabo eAceh.
Ngowama-2005: Uxanduva lweenyikima ezinamandla lwahlasela unxweme olusentshona yeSumatra ngasekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kuka-Aprili.
Amakhulu afa kwisiqithi saseNias, kunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngowama-2006: Umonakalo omkhulu onamandla angama-6.8 wahlasela emazantsi eJava, esona siqithi sinabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, waza wabangela ukuba kubekho i-tsunami eyaqhekeza unxweme olusemzantsi, yabulala abantu abamalunga nama-700.
Ngowama-2009: Kwabakho inyikima enamandla ayi-7.6 kufutshane nesixeko sasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona yeSumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngowama-2010: Inyikima enamandla angama-7.5 yahlasela esinye seziqithi zaseMentawai, kufutshane neSumatra, yabangela ukuba kubekho i-tsunami yeemitha ezili-10 ezatshabalalisa amashumi eedolophana zaza zabulala abantu abamalunga nama-300.
Ngowama-2016: Inyikima enzulu yahlasela iPidi Jaya regency e-Aceh, yabangela umonakalo kunye nexhala njengoko abantu bakhunjuzwa yindawo eyayitshatyalaliswe yinyikima ne-tsunami ka-2004.
Akukho tsunami yabangelayo ngeli xesha, kodwa ngaphezu kwe-100 yabulawa zizakhiwo eziwileyo.
Ngo-2018: Iinyikima ezinkulu zenzeka kwisiqithi sokhenketho saseLombok eIndonesia, zabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-500, uninzi lwabo lwalusemazantsi esiqithi.
Le nyikima yatshayela amawaka ezakhiwo yaza yashiya amawaka abakhenkethi engakwazi ukuya.
Unyana Omdala KaSarah Palin Wabanjwa Ngenxa Yentlondi Yasekhaya
UTrac Palin, unyana omdala owayengumlawuli waseAlaska nomgqatswa oyiphini likaMongameli uSarah Palin, ubanjwe etyholwa ngokuhlaselwa.
UPalin, oneminyaka engama-29 ubudala waseWasilla, eAlaska, wabanjwa ngokusolwa ngokuba ebekhe waphathwa ngogonyamelo lwentsapho, engenelele kwingxelo yobundlobongela basekhaya yaye enxamnye nokubanjwa, ngokutsho kwengxelo ekhutshwe ngoMgqibelo ngamajoni aseAlaska.
Ngokwengxelo yamapolisa, xa umhlobo wakhe wazama ukubiza amapolisa ukuze axele ulwaphulo-mthetho oluthethwayo, wamthabatha ifowuni yakhe.
IPalin igcinwe kwindawo yokugcina amatyala eMat-Su yaye igcinwe kwibond engaqinisekanga engama-500 eedola, kubika iKTUU.
Lo mntu wabonakala enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, apho wathi "akanatyala, ngokuqinisekileyo" xa ebuzwa ngesibheno sakhe, inethiwekhi yaxela.
UPalin unetyala lokwaphula umthetho ezintathu, nto leyo ethetha ukuba unokubanjwa unyaka omnye aze anikwe imali eyi-250 000 yeedola.
Kwakhona uye watyholwa ngesityholo sobugwenxa, esihlawuliswa usuku entolongweni kunye ne-2 000 yeedola.
Asingowona mzuzu wokuqala ukubekwa amatyala okubulala uPalin.
NgoDisemba 2017, watyholwa ngokuhlasela uyise, uTodd Palin.
Unina, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuba abike ngokuhlaselwa.
Eli tyala likwiNkundla yamajoni aseBhetreya yaseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016 watyholwa ngokuhlaselwa ekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yobundlobongela basekhaya, kunye nokuba nesibhamu ngelixa enxilile ngokunxulumene nesiganeko.
Intombi yakhe yathi yamtyakatya ebusweni.
USarah Palin wagxekwa ngamaqela amajoni asebugxwayibeni ngo-2016 emva kokunxibelelanisa ukuziphatha konogonyamelo konyana wakhe ne-PTSD evela kwinkonzo yakhe e-Iraq.
Inyikima yaseIndonesia ne-tsunami: Kwafa amakhulu abantu
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 baye bafa emva kokuba inyikima yenzakalise isiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi ngoLwesihlanu.
Inyikima enamandla angama-7.5 yabangela ukuba kubekho i - tsunami yaza yatshatyalalisa amawaka amakhaya.
Umbane nonxibelelwano ziyaphela yaye inani labantu abafayo liza kunyuka kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Inyikima yahlasela iSulawesi eseMntla-mpuma kwikomkhulu laseIndonesia, iJakarta.
Iividiyo ziyasasazeka kwiinethiwekhi zentlalo ezibonisa umzuzu wempembelelo.
Amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene kumsitho waselunxwemeni kwisixeko sasePalu xa kwaqhambuka itsunami elunxwemeni.
Abaphikisi baseburhulumenteni bafuna isigwebo sokufa esinqabileyo kumntu osolwayo kwi-NYC
Abaphikisi baseNew York bafuna isigwebo sokufa sikaSayfullo Saipov, osolwayo kwi-terror attack yaseNew York ebulala abantu abasibhozo - isigwebo esinqabileyo esingazange senziwe kweli lizwe ngenxa yolwaphulo-mthetho lwe-federal ukususela ngowe-1953.
USaipov, oneminyaka engama-30 ubudala, kuthiwa wasebenzisa iLori yokuqesha iHome Depot ukwenza uhlaselo kwindlela yebhayisekile ecaleni kweWest Side Highway eMzantsi Manhattan, esusa abakhweli kunye nabaqhubi bebhayisekile endleleni yakhe ngo-Oktobha.
Ukuze kuxolelwe isigwebo sokufa, abachubi-mthetho baya kufuneka bangqine ukuba uSaipov "wabulala ngabom" la maxhoba asibhozo waza "wabangela" ukwenzakala emzimbeni, ngokutsho kwesaziso senjongo yokufuna isigwebo sokufa, esifakwe kwiSithili saseMzantsi saseNew York.
Ngokutsho kwexwebhu leNkundla, zombini ezi zityholo zinokugwetywa ukufa.
Kwiiveki emva kokuhlaselwa, iJury enkulu yase-Federal yabeka isityholo esimalunga nama-22 kuSaipov, esasiquka amatyala asibhozo obulele abantu besebenzisa imali yokunyusa, ngokuqhelekileyo asetyenziswa ngamagqwetha ase-Federal kumatyala olwaphulo-mthetho oluhleliweyo, kunye netyala lobundlobongela nokutshatyalaliswa kwezithuthi.
Ababhekisi bathi lo mlo wawufuna "ukucwangciswa nokucwangciswa kwangaphambili", besithi indlela uSaipov awawenza ngayo "yayintlekisa, inkohlakalo yaye inkohlakalo".
"USayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wenzakalisa, wenzakalisa, waza walahlekelwa ziintsapho nabahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicolas Cleves, uAnn-Laure Decadt, uDarren Drake, uAriel Erlij, uHernan Ferruchi, uHernan Diego Mendoza, noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco", itsho isaziso senjongo.
Amahlanu kula maxhoba ayengama tourist avela eArgentina.
Sele kudlule iminyaka elishumi ukususela oko iSithili saseMzantsi saseNew York sagqibela ukumangalela ityala lokufa.
Ummangalelwa, uKhalid Barnes, wagwetywa ngokubulala abaxhasi ababini beziyobisi kodwa ekugqibeleni wagwetywa ubomi bonke entolongweni ngoSeptemba 2009.
Ixesha lokugqibela isigwebo sokufa senziwa kwicala laseNew York lalingu-1953 kuJulius noEthel Rosenberg, isibini esitshatileyo esabulawa emva kokuba sigwetyelwe ukubhenela kwiSoviet Union ngexesha leMfazwe Yomlomo kwiminyaka emibini ngaphambili.
Bobabini oonyana bakaRosenberg babulawa sisihlalo sombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
Ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu enkundla, uSaipov, odabuka eUzbekistan, wabonisa ukungabi nazintloni kwiintsuku neenyanga emva kokuhlaselwa.
Amapolisa athi wachazela abaphandi ukuba wayeziva ekhululekile ngenxa yoko wakwenzayo.
USaipov uxelele abasemagunyeni ukuba waphefumlelwa ukuba enze lo mlo emva kokubukela iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe, ngokutsho kwesimangalo.
Kwakhona wacela ukuba ibhanti ye-ISIS ibekwe kwigumbi lakhe lasebhedlele, ipolisa lathi.
Uye wavuma ukuba akanatyala kwizityholo ezingama-22.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabaphembeleli bakarhulumente abamele uSaipov, uthe "kucacile ukuba badanile" ngesigqibo sobheno.
UPatton wathi: "Sicinga ukuba isigqibo sokufuna isohlwayo sokufa kunokuba samkele isigwebo sokubekwa ityala ubomi bonke entolongweni ngaphandle kokukhululwa siya kuqhubeka sisenza ukuba bonke ababandakanyekileyo babe buhlungu ngenxa yezi ziganeko".
Iqela lokhuselo likaSaipov ngaphambili lalicele amagqwetha ukuba angafuni isigwebo sokufa.
Indlu yowiso-mthetho yamaTory ithi uNIGEL FARAGE kufuneka abekwe ukuba abe ngumlawuli weengxoxo zeBrexit
UNigel Farage wafunga 'ukuhambisa umkhosi wabantu' namhlanje ngexesha lokuchasa kwinkomfa yamaTory.
Lo owayesakuba yinkokeli ye-Ukip wathi abezopolitiko kufuneka 'baziva beshushu' kuba befuna ukulawula i-euro-sceptics - njengoko omnye wabameli bakaTheresa May wathi ufanele abe ngumlawuli weengxoxo ne-EU.
Umongameli we-backbencher wolondolozo-mbono uPeter Bone wathi kwiMatshi eBirmingham ukuba uMnu Farage wayengumGcini-mthetho weBrexit, i-UK 'yayingayi kuba khona' ngoku.
Kodwa umceli mngeni uMnu May ajongene nawo ekuvumelaniseni amacandelo akhe ahlukeneyo agxininiswe ngamaTories alwela ukuhlala ngokujoyina umbhikisho ohlukileyo wokuchasana neBrexit kwisixeko.
UMongameli uZuma ulwela ukugcina isicwangciso sakhe sokwenza imvumelwano neChequers sisemgangathweni phakathi kweentlaselo ezivela kuma-Brexiteers, kuma-Remainers nakwi-EU.
Amaqabane athi uza kuqhubeka nokuzama ukufikelela kwisivumelwano neBrussels phezu kwayo nje imiphumo emibi - aze anyanzele ama-Eurosceptics kunye namaLearks ukuba akhethe phakathi kwepakethe yakhe kunye 'nentlekele'.
UMnu Bone uxelele umbutho we-Leave Means Leave eSolihull ukuba ufuna 'ukuqhawula i-Chequers'.
Wacebisa ukuba uMnu Farage kufuneka abe ngumlingane kwaye anikwe uxanduva lweengxoxo neBrussels.
Wathi: 'Ukuba wayelawula, ngoku ngephantse saphuma.
Ilungu leNdlu yaseWellingborough yongezelela: 'Ndiza kumela iBrexit kodwa kufuneka silahle iChequers.'
Echaza indlela ayichasa ngayo i-EU, wathi: 'Asizange silwe iimfazwe zehlabathi ukuze sibe ngabathobekileyo.
Sifuna ukwenza imithetho yethu kwilizwe lethu.'
UMnu Bone uligatyile icebiso lokuba uluvo loluntu lutshintshile ukususela kuvotelo lwango-2016: "Ingcamango yokuba abantu baseBritani batshintshile ingqondo kwaye bafuna ukuhlala ayinyani ngokupheleleyo".
Umxhasi weBrexiteer Tory uAndrea Jenkyns naye wayekho kuloo ntlanganiso, esithi kumajelo eendaba: 'Ndiyathetha nje: Ndunankulu, phulaphula abantu.
'I-Chequers ayithandwa ngabantu ngokubanzi, abachasi abayi kuvota kuyo, ayithandwa liqela lethu kunye neenkokeli zethu ezenza ukuba siphakame ezitalatweni size sikhethwe kuqala.
Nceda ushiye i-Chequers uze uqalise ukuphulaphula.'
Kwisigidimi esibhekiswe kuMnu May, wongezelela wathi: 'Oongqongqoshe bayazigcina izicelo zabo xa bezigcina izithembiso zabo.'
UMnu Farage uthe abapolitiki kufuneka benze ukuba 'bazive zishushu' ukuba befuna ukulahlekisa isigqibo esenziwe kwi-referendum ka-2016.
Wathi: 'Ngoku, lo mba uthetha ngokuthembana phakathi kwethu - abantu - kunye neqela lethu lezopolitiko.'
'Bazama ukukhohlisa iBrexit kwaye silapha namhlanje ukuxelela ukuba 'asiyi kukuvumela ukuba usinde ngokwenza oko.'
Kwisigidimi esiya kwisihlwele esinomdla wongezelela: 'Ndifuna niyenze icawa yethu yezopolitiko, esekude nokungcatsha iBrexit, iziva ishushu.
'Siqokelela umkhosi wabantu beli lizwe owasinika uloyiso kwiBrexit kwaye awusoze uphumle de sibe lilizwe elizimeleyo, elizilawulayo nelizigqabileyo laseUnited Kingdom.'
Okwangoku, abahlali bahambela eBirmingham ngaphambi kokuba benze umngcelele weeyure ezimbini kumbindi wesixeko.
Iqela elincinane lezisebenzi laphakamisa amabhanela amaTories Against Brexit emva kokumiliselwa kweli qela kule mpelaveki.
Umlingane weqela lezabasebenzi uLord Adonis wagculela amaConservatives ngenxa yeengxaki zokhuseleko abajamelana nazo ngeapp yeqela xa kwaqaliswa inkomfa.
"Aba bantu basixelela ukuba banokufumana iinkqubo ze-IT kunye nayo yonke iteknoloji yeCanada plus plus, yomda ongenazingxaki, yorhwebo olukhululekileyo olungenamida eIreland", wongezelela.
'Yinto eyonakalisayo.
Akukho nto ithethwa ngokuba yiBrexit elungileyo", wongezelela.
UWarren uceba 'ukujonga ngenyameko' ukuba ngumongameli
US Senator Elizabeth Warren uthi uza "kujonga ngenyameko ukuba uza kuba ngumongameli" emva konyulo lukaNovemba.
IBoston Globe ithi uMassachusetts Democrat wathetha ngekamva lakhe ngexesha lokulawula kwindlu kawonke-wonke kwintshona yeMassachusetts ngoMgqibelo.
UWarren, ogxeka uMongameli uDonald Trump rhoqo, ukhuphisana nokhetho kwakhona ngoNovemba ngokuchasene neRepublican State Rep. uGeoff Diehl, owayengumongameli wephulo likaTrump eMassachusetts ngo-2016.
Ube ngundoqo kwiingcamango zokuba angamelana noTrump ngo-2020.
Umsitho womgqibelo emva kwemini eHolyoke waba yintlanganiso yakhe yama-36 kunye nabemi basebenzisa ifomathi yendlu karhulumente ukususela oko uTrump wangena esihlalweni.
Omnye owayekho wambuza ukuba uyafuna na ukuba ngumongameli.
