I-Gran Prix yaseRashiya: ULewis Hamilton ufikelela kwincopho yehlabathi emva kokuba iqela lifumene umyalelo wokumnika uloyiso phezu kukaSebastian Vettel
Kwacaca ukususela mzuzu uValtteri Bottas afumana isidanga phambi kukaLewis Hamilton ngoMgqibelo ukuba imiyalelo yeqela leMercedes yayiza kudlala indima enkulu kulo mgqatswa.
