UMongameli waseMerika uDonald Trump, wenza isilumkiso sokuqala ekuqaleni konyaka ngokuhlawula irhafu kwizithuthi eziphambili zaseTshayina kuquka iipaneli zelanga, intsimbi nealuminium.
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo yayikukuqalisa kwale veki, kuba imirhumo emitsha ichaphazela iimpahla ezixabisa iidola ezingama-200 ezigidi (i-150 ezigidi ze-Â£), ngokufanelekileyo irhafu yeempahla zonke eziza e-US zisuka e-China.
I-Beijing iye yaphendula ngamaxesha onke, kutshanje iye yahlawula amaxabiso angama-5 ukuya kuma-10 ekhulwini kwiimveliso zaseMerika ezingama-60 ezigidi zeedola.
I-China ithembise ukuba iya kuhambelana ne-US, yaye akubonakali ngathi i-economy yesibini ngobukhulu ehlabathini iya kubetha amehlo kungekudala.
Ukubangela iWashington ukuba ihoxe kuthetha ukuvumela iimfuno, kodwa ukuzithoba esidlangalaleni eU.S. kuya kuba lihlazo kakhulu kuMongameli waseTshayina uXi Jinping.
Noko ke, iingcali zithi ukuba iBeijing iyakwazi ukudlala amakhadi ayo ngokufanelekileyo, uxinzelelo lweMfazwe yoRhwebo yase-US lunokuxhasa iChina ngokuqinisekileyo kwixesha elide ngokunciphisa ukuxhomekeka phakathi kwezoqoqosho zimbini.
