Urhulumente uyaqhubeka nokuhlaziya iindawo ezonakaliswe ngabagqugqisi ukuze abuyisele imeko eqhelekileyo.
Ngoku kukho zonke iimeko zokubuyela ngokuzithandela kweembacu kwilizwe abaphulukene nalo ngenxa yobugebenga kunye namanyathelo oqoqosho olunye olujolise kubomi babo bemihla ngemihla nakubomi babo.
