IYurophu iphumelela kwiRyder Cup eParis
Iqela laseYurophu liphumelele i-2018 Ryder Cup libetha iQela lase-USA ngamanqaku okugqibela e-16.5 ukuya ku-10.5 kwiLe Golf National ngaphandle kweParis, eFransi.
I-US ngoku ilahlekelwe ngamaxesha amathandathu ngokulandelelana kumhlaba waseYurophu kwaye ayizange iphumelele iRyder Cup eYurophu ukususela ngo-1993.
IYurophu yafumana isithsaba xa iqela likaputeni waseDenmark uThomas Bjorn lafikelela kwi-14.5 amanqaku ayefuneka ukuze libethe iUnited States.
Inkwenkwezi yaseMerika uPhil Mickelson, owalwa nzima uninzi lomdlalo, wafaka i-tee shot yakhe emanzini kwi-par-3 16th hole, ebanikezela umdlalo wakhe kuFrancesco Molinari.
Umdlali wegalufa waseItali uMolinari wakhazimla kuwo onke amaqela akhe, waba ngumdlali omnye kwabane owakha wahamba nge-5-0-0 ukususela ekuqalisweni kwenkqubo yangoku yomdyarho ngowe-1979.
UmAmerican uJordan Spieth waphume 5 & 4 ngumdlali ophantsi kwiqela laseYurophu, uThorbjorn Olesen waseDenmark.
Umdlali ophambili ehlabathini, uDustin Johnson, wehla 2 no-1 kuIan Poulter waseNgilani onokuthi wadlala kwiRyder Cup yakhe yokugqibela.
Umakadebona kwiiNdebe zeRyder ezisibhozo, uSergio Garcia waseSpain waba ngowona mdlali uphumelele kakhulu eYurophu ngamaxesha onke nge-25.5 amanqaku.
"Ngokuqhelekileyo andikhali kodwa namhlanje andinakukwazi ukuyeka.
Kube ngunyaka onzima.
Ndiyambulela gqitha uThomas ngokundikhetha nokundikholelwa.
Ndivuya gqitha, ndivuya gqitha kuba ndiyifumene le ndebe.
Iqela limele ukuba lilincedile, kwaye ndiyavuya ndakwazi ukunceda", watsho uGarcia enovelwano emva kokuphumelela kweYurophu.
Udlulisela itompu kumhlobo wakhe uJohn Ram owabetha ingqungquthela yegalufa yaseMerika iTiger Woods 2&1 kumdlalo we-singles ngeCawa.
