UWoods uphulukene nayo yonke imidlalo yakhe emine eFransi kwaye ngoku unerekhodi ye-13-21-3 yeRyder Cup.
Isithethiso esingaqhelekanga somnye wabadlali abakhulu bexesha lonke, owathi waphumelela izihloko ezili-14 ezikhulu emva kukaJack Nicklaus.
Iqela lase-USA lalisoloko lisilwa yonke iiveki ukuze lifumane i-fairways ngaphandle kukaPatrick Reed, uJustin Thomas noTony Finau, abadlala igalofu ephezulu kulo lonke itumente.
U-US Captain Jim Furyk wathetha emva kokwenza into edimazayo kwiqela lakhe, "Ndizingca ngala madoda, alwa.
Kwakukho ixesha namhlanje ekuseni xa sasisabela eYurophu.
Sasilahlile.
Isigcina-ntloko kuThomas.
Ungumthetheli omkhulu.
Bonke abadlali bakhe abali-12 badlala kakuhle.
Siza kudibana kwakhona, ndiza kusebenza nePGA yaseMerika neKomiti yethu yeNdebe yeRyder size siqhubele phambili.
Ndibathanda aba bafana abali-12 yaye ndiyazingca ngokuba nguKaputeni.
Kufuneka uziphucule.
Saqhutywa".
